很长很长很长很长\r\n            很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长\r\n            很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长很长\r\n            很长很长很长很长很长\r\n        </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n.test-1{\r\n    border: 1px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n        \r\n    -moz-column-count: auto;\r\n\t-webkit-column-count: auto;\r\n\tcolumn-count: auto;\r\n\t-moz-column-width: 193px;\r\n\t-webkit-column-width: 193px;\r\n\tcolumn-width: 193px;\r\n}\r\n.test-2{\r\n    border: 1px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n    \r\n    -moz-column-count:3;\r\n    -webkit-column-count:3;\r\n    column-count:3;\r\n}\r\n.test-3{\r\n    border: 1px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n    \r\n    -moz-column-count:3;\r\n    -webkit-column-count:3;\r\n    column-count:3;\r\n    \r\n    -webkit-column-gap: 40px;\r\n    -moz-column-gap: 40px;\r\n    column-gap: 40px;\r\n}    \r\n.test-4{\r\n    border: 1px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n    \r\n    -moz-column-count:3;\r\n    -webkit-column-count:3;\r\n    column-count:3;\r\n\r\n    -moz-column-rule: 5px solid red;\r\n    -webkit-column-rule: 5px solid red;\r\n    column-rule: 5px solid red;\r\n}\r\n.test-5{\r\n    border: 1px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n    \r\n    -moz-column-count:3;\r\n    -webkit-column-count:3;\r\n    column-count:3;\r\n}\r\n.test-5 h4{\r\n    -moz-column-span: all;\r\n    -webkit-column-span: all;\r\n    column-span: all;\r\n}','','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js','CSS3 实验-文字多列布局',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',2,NULL,'2013-11-19 16:11:00',NULL,NULL,'2,8','CSS3,CSS');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (124,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <div class=\"test\">\r\n        <h3 class=\"ribbon\">Ribbon 效果</h3>\r\n        \r\n        需要为目标元素添加 position: relative;\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n<!--     <div class=\"test\">\r\n        <div class=\"tab\">\r\n            <h4 class=\"tab_head\"></h4>\r\n            <div class=\"tab_content\"></div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"tab\">\r\n            <h4 class=\"tab_head\"></h4>\r\n            <div class=\"tab_content\"></div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"tab\">\r\n            <h4 class=\"tab_head\"></h4>\r\n            <div class=\"tab_content\"></div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"tab\">\r\n            <h4 class=\"tab_head\"></h4>\r\n            <div class=\"tab_content\"></div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div> -->\r\n    \r\n   <!--  <div id=\"cssTabs\">\r\n        <div id=\"tab1\" class=\"uiTab\">\r\n            <h3 class=\"tabHead\">Header for Tab1</h3>\r\n            <div class=\"tabContent\">Content for Tab1</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"tab2\" class=\"uiTab\">\r\n            <h3 class=\"tabHead\">Header for Tab2</h3>\r\n            <div class=\"tabContent\">Content for Tab2</div>\r\n        </div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n        <div id=\"tab3\" class=\"uiTab\">\r\n            <h3 class=\"tabHead\">Header for Tab3</h3>\r\n            <div class=\"tabContent\">Content for Tab3</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div> -->\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.test{\r\n    float: left;\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    width: 400px;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n    border: 1px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 50px;\r\n    background: white;\r\n}\r\n.ribbon{\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    left: -15px;\r\n    right: -15px;\r\n    top: 10px;\r\n    \r\n    min-height: 30px;\r\n    \r\n    background: #e0e0e0;\r\n    \r\n    -moz-box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);\r\n    -khtml-box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);\r\n    -webkit-box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);\r\n    box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    line-height: 150%;\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n.ribbon:before,\r\n.ribbon:after{\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    bottom: -15px;\r\n    z-index: -1;\r\n    width: 0;\r\n    height: 0;\r\n    \r\n    border: 15px solid transparent;\r\n    content: \"\";\r\n}\r\n.ribbon:before{\r\n    left: -15px;\r\n    border-right-color: #e0e0e0;\r\n}\r\n.ribbon:after{\r\n    right: -15px;\r\n    border-left-color: #e0e0e0;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* .tab{\r\n}\r\n.tab_head{\r\n    float: left;\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    z-index: 3;\r\n            \r\n    height: 25px;\r\n    min-width: 60px;\r\n            \r\n    border:5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    border-bottom: 0;\r\n    border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;\r\n    margin: 0 10px 0 0;\r\n    \r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n.tab_content{\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    bottom: 0;\r\n    top: 30px;\r\n    z-index: 2;\r\n    \r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    \r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n} */\r\n\r\n/* \r\nCSS Tabs style\r\n#cssTabs {\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    width: 600px;\r\n    height: 290px;\r\n    margin: 0 auto;\r\n}\r\n.tabHead {\r\n    font-weight: normal;\r\n    margin: 0;\r\n    padding: 5px;\r\n    height: 30px;\r\n    line-height: 30px;\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n    border: 1px solid #000;\r\n    border-width: 1px 1px 0;\r\n    -moz-border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;\r\n    -webkit-border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;\r\n    border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;\r\n    width: 140px;\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    left: 0;\r\n    top: 0;\r\n    background: #fff;\r\n    cursor: pointer;\r\n}\r\n.tabContent {\r\n    padding: 10px 20px;\r\n    background: #fff;\r\n    border: 1px solid #000;\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    top: 40px;\r\n    left: 0;\r\n    height: 230px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    opacity: 0;\r\n    filter: alpha(opacity=0);\r\n    -ms-filter:\"progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.Alpha(Opacity=0)\";  \r\n    -webkit-transition : opacity 0.5s ease-in 0.218s;\r\n    -moz-transition : opacity 0.5s ease-in 0.218s;\r\n    -o-transition : opacity 0.5s ease-in 0.218s;\r\n    -ms-transition : opacity 0.5s ease-in 0.218s;\r\n    transition : opacity 0.5s ease-in 0.218s;\r\n}\r\n#tab1 .tabHead {\r\n    z-index: 3;\r\n}\r\n#tab2 .tabHead {\r\n    left: 155px;\r\n    z-index: 1;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#tab3 .tabHead {\r\n    left: 310px;\r\n    z-index: 1;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#tab1 .tabContent {\r\n    z-index: 2;\r\n    opacity: 1;\r\n    filter: alpha(opacity=100);\r\n    -ms-filter:\"progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.Alpha(Opacity=100)\";\r\n}\r\n\r\n#tab1:hover h3,\r\n#tab1:focus h3,\r\n#tab1:active h3,\r\n#tab2:hover h3,\r\n#tab2:focus h3,\r\n#tab2:active h3,\r\n#tab3:hover h3,\r\n#tab3:focus h3,\r\n#tab3:active h3 {\r\n    z-index: 4;\r\n    font-weight: bold;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#tab1:hover .tabContent,\r\n#tab1:focus .tabContent,\r\n#tab1:active .tabContent,\r\n#tab2:hover .tabContent,\r\n#tab2:focus .tabContent,\r\n#tab2:active .tabContent,\r\n#tab3:hover .tabContent,\r\n#tab3:focus .tabContent,\r\n#tab3:active .tabContent {            \r\n    z-index: 3;\r\n    opacity: 1;\r\n    filter: alpha(opacity=100);\r\n    -ms-filter:\"progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.Alpha(Opacity=100)\";\r\n} */','','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js','CSS 示例-Ribbon 效果',NULL,'../image/preview/ribbon.jpg',2,NULL,'2013-11-20 15:05:33',NULL,NULL,'48,4','原创,UI');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (125,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>CSS3 filter 属性</h3>\r\n    <p>\r\n        CSS3 filter 和 css filter 完全不同，更不是 IE 滤镜\r\n        <br />\r\n        filter 主要是运用在图片上，以实现一些特效，也能运用于 video 上\r\n        <br />\r\n        现在只有 webkit 内核浏览器支持\r\n        <br />\r\n        <br />参考教程\r\n        <a href=\"http://www.w3cplus.com/css3/ten-effects-with-css3-filter\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n            http://www.w3cplus.com/css3/ten-effects-with-css3-filter\r\n        </a>\r\n    </p>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n        <figcaption>原始图像</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"grayscale\" />\r\n        <figcaption>grayscale 灰度</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"sepia\" />\r\n        <figcaption>sepia</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"saturate\" />\r\n        <figcaption>saturate 饱和度</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"hue-rotate\" />\r\n        <figcaption>hue-rotate 色相旋转</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"invert\" />\r\n        <figcaption>invert 反色</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"opacity\" />\r\n        <figcaption>opacity 透明度</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"brightness\" />\r\n        <figcaption>brightness 亮度</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"contrast\" />\r\n        <figcaption>contrast 对比度</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"blur\" />\r\n        <figcaption>blur 模糊</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"drop-shadow\" />\r\n        <figcaption>drop-shadow 阴影</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n    \r\n    <figure>\r\n        <img src=\"../image/demo/demoImage-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"custom\" />\r\n        <figcaption>多种效果应用</figcaption>\r\n    </figure>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.test{\r\n    border: 1px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n}\r\nfigure{\r\n    float: left;\r\n}\r\nimg{\r\n    height: 150px;\r\n    width:240px;\r\n    \r\n    border:solid #fff;\r\n    border-width:6px 6px 40px 6px;\r\n    margin: 5px;\r\n    \r\n    background:#000;\r\n    \r\n    box-shadow:1px 1px 5px #333;\r\n}\r\nfigcaption{\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    \r\n    top: -40px;\r\n    left: 40px;\r\n}\r\n.grayscale{\r\n    -webkit-filter: grayscale(1);\r\n    -moz-filter: grayscale(1);\r\n    -ms-filter: grayscale(1);\r\n    -o-filter: grayscale(1);\r\n    filter: grayscale(1);\r\n}\r\n.sepia{\r\n    -webkit-filter: sepia(1);\r\n    -moz-filter: sepia(1);\r\n    -ms-filter: sepia(1);\r\n    -o-filter: sepia(1);\r\n    filter: sepia(1);\r\n}\r\n.saturate{\r\n    -webkit-filter: saturate(0.5);\r\n    -moz-filter: saturate(0.5);\r\n    -ms-filter: saturate(0.5);\r\n    -o-filter: saturate(0.5);\r\n    filter: saturate(0.5);\r\n}\r\n.hue-rotate{\r\n    -webkit-filter: hue-rotate(90deg);\r\n    -moz-filter: hue-rotate(90deg);\r\n    -ms-filter: hue-rotate(90deg);\r\n    -o-filter: hue-rotate(90deg);\r\n    filter: hue-rotate(90deg);\r\n}\r\n.invert{\r\n    -webkit-filter: invert(1);\r\n    -moz-filter: invert(1);\r\n    -ms-filter: invert(1);\r\n    -o-filter: invert(1);\r\n    filter: invert(1);\r\n}\r\n.opacity{\r\n    -webkit-filter: opacity(.2);\r\n    -moz-filter: opacity(.2);\r\n    -ms-filter: opacity(.2);\r\n    -o-filter: opacity(.2);\r\n    filter: opacity(.2);\r\n}\r\n.brightness{\r\n    -webkit-filter: brightness(.5);\r\n    -moz-filter: brightness(.5);\r\n    -ms-filter: brightness(.5);\r\n    -o-filter: brightness(.5);\r\n    filter: brightness(.5);\r\n}\r\n.contrast{\r\n    -webkit-filter: contrast(2);\r\n    -moz-filter: contrast(2);\r\n    -ms-filter: contrast(2);\r\n    -o-filter: contrast(2);\r\n    filter: contrast(2);\r\n}\r\n.blur{\r\n    -webkit-filter: blur(3px);\r\n    -moz-filter: blur(3px);\r\n    -ms-filter: blur(3px);\r\n    -o-filter: blur(3px);\r\n    filter: blur(3px);\r\n}\r\n.drop-shadow{\r\n    box-shadow: none;\r\n    -webkit-filter: drop-shadow(5px 5px 5px #ccc);\r\n    -moz-filter: drop-shadow(5px 5px 5px #ccc);\r\n    -ms-filter: drop-shadow(5px 5px 5px #ccc);\r\n    -o-filter: drop-shadow(5px 5px 5px #ccc);\r\n    filter: drop-shadow(5px 5px 5px #ccc);\r\n}\r\n.custom{\r\n    -webkit-filter: saturate(5) hue-rotate(500deg) grayscale(0.3) sepia(0.7) contrast(1.5) invert(0.2);\r\n    -moz-filter: saturate(5) hue-rotate(500deg) grayscale(0.3) sepia(0.7) contrast(1.5) invert(0.2);\r\n    -ms-filter: saturate(5) hue-rotate(500deg) grayscale(0.3) sepia(0.7) contrast(1.5) invert(0.2);\r\n    -o-filter: saturate(5) hue-rotate(500deg) grayscale(0.3) sepia(0.7) contrast(1.5) invert(0.2);\r\n    filter: saturate(5) hue-rotate(500deg) grayscale(0.3) sepia(0.7) contrast(1.5) invert(0.2);\r\n}','','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js','CSS3 实验-filter 属性',NULL,'../image/preview/filter.jpg',2,NULL,'2013-11-20 17:07:29',NULL,NULL,'2,8','CSS3,CSS');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (126,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>CSS3 提示信息</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\" class=\"form-horizontal\">\r\n        <fieldset>\r\n            <div class=\"control-group\">\r\n                <label for=\"email\" class=\"control-label\">E-Mail:</label>\r\n                <div class=\"controls controls-inline\">\r\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" />\r\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\">Please Input Your Email!</span>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"control-group\">\r\n                <label for=\"password\" class=\"control-label\">Password:</label>\r\n                <div class=\"controls controls-inline\">\r\n                    <input type=\"password\" id=\"password\" />\r\n                    <span class=\"help-inline\">Please Input Your Password!</span>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\t\t\t \r\n        </fieldset>\r\n        <fieldset>\r\n            <div class=\"control-group\">\r\n                <label for=\"email2\" class=\"control-label\">E-Mail:</label>\r\n                <div class=\"controls controls-block\">\r\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email2\" />\r\n                    <span class=\"help-block\">Please Input Your Email!</span>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"control-group\">\r\n                <label for=\"password2\" class=\"control-label\">Password:</label>\r\n                <div class=\"controls controls-block\">\r\n                    <input type=\"password\" id=\"password2\" >\r\n                    <span class=\"help-block\">Please Input Your Password!</span>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\t\t\t \r\n        </fieldset>\r\n    </form>\t\r\n    \r\n<!--     <label class=\"focus-tips hidden\" data-focus=\"提示信息\">填写信息\r\n        <input type=\"text\" name=\"\" id=\"\"  />\r\n    </label> -->\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n/*\r\n.focus-tips{\r\nfloat: left;\r\nposition: relative;\r\n}\r\n.focus-tips:before{\r\nposition: absolute;\r\n\r\ntop: 50%;\r\nright: -15px;\r\n\r\nborder: 10px solid transparent;\r\nborder-color: transparent #000 transparent transparent;\r\nmargin-top: -15px;\r\n\r\ncolor: #fff;\r\ncontent: \"\";\r\n}\r\n.focus-tips:after{\r\nposition: absolute;\r\n\r\ntop: 50%;\r\nright: -115px;\r\n\r\nheight: 40px;\r\nmin-width: 100px;\r\n\r\nborder-radius: 5px;\r\nmargin-top: -25px;\r\nbackground: #000;\r\n\r\ncolor: #fff;\r\nline-height: 40px;\r\ntext-align: center;\r\ncontent: attr(data-focus);\r\n}\r\n\r\n.focus-tips:focus:before{\r\n\r\n}\r\n.focus-tips:focus:after{\r\n\r\n}\r\n*/\r\n\r\nform {\r\n    margin: 20px 0 18px;\r\n}\r\nfieldset {\r\n    padding: 0;\r\n    margin: 0;\r\n    border: 0;\r\n}\r\nlabel,\r\ninput,\r\nbutton{\r\n    font-size: 13px;\r\n    font-weight: normal;\r\n    line-height: 18px;\r\n}\r\ninput,\r\nbutton{\r\n    font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n}\r\nlabel {\r\n    display: block;\r\n    margin-bottom: 5px;\r\n    color: #333333;\r\n}\r\ninput{\r\n    display: inline-block;\r\n    width: 210px;\r\n    height: 18px;\r\n    padding: 4px;\r\n    margin-bottom: 9px;\r\n    font-size: 13px;\r\n    line-height: 18px;\r\n    color: #555555;\r\n    border: 1px solid #cccccc;\r\n    -webkit-border-radius: 3px;\r\n    -moz-border-radius: 3px;\r\n    border-radius: 3px;\r\n}\r\ninput[type=\"button\"],\r\ninput[type=\"reset\"],\r\ninput[type=\"submit\"] {\r\n    width: auto;\r\n    height: auto;\r\n}\r\ninput {\r\n    -webkit-box-shadow: inset 0 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075);\r\n        -moz-box-shadow: inset 0 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075);\r\n        box-shadow: inset 0 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075);\r\n        -webkit-transition: border linear 0.2s, box-shadow linear 0.2s;\r\n        -moz-transition: border linear 0.2s, box-shadow linear 0.2s;\r\n        -ms-transition: border linear 0.2s, box-shadow linear 0.2s;\r\n        -o-transition: border linear 0.2s, box-shadow linear 0.2s;\r\n        transition: border linear 0.2s, box-shadow linear 0.2s;\r\n    }\r\n    input:focus,\r\n        textarea:focus {\r\n            border-color: rgba(82, 168, 236, 0.8);\r\n            -webkit-box-shadow: inset 0 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075), 0 0 8px rgba(82, 168, 236, 0.6);\r\n            -moz-box-shadow: inset 0 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075), 0 0 8px rgba(82, 168, 236, 0.6);\r\n            box-shadow: inset 0 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075), 0 0 8px rgba(82, 168, 236, 0.6);\r\n            outline: 0;\r\n            outline: thin dotted \\9;\r\n        }\r\n        input{\r\n            margin-left: 0;\r\n        }\r\n        input:focus:required:invalid,\r\n        textarea:focus:required:invalid,\r\n        select:focus:required:invalid {\r\n            color: #b94a48;\r\n            border-color: #ee5f5b;\r\n        }\r\n        input:focus:required:invalid:focus,\r\n        textarea:focus:required:invalid:focus,\r\n        select:focus:required:invalid:focus {\r\n            border-color: #e9322d;\r\n            -webkit-box-shadow: 0 0 6px #f8b9b7;\r\n            -moz-box-shadow: 0 0 6px #f8b9b7;\r\n            box-shadow: 0 0 6px #f8b9b7;\r\n        }\r\n        :-moz-placeholder {\r\n            color: #999999;\r\n        }\r\n        ::-webkit-input-placeholder {\r\n            color: #999999;\r\n        }\r\n        .help-block,\r\n.help-inline {\r\n    color: #555555;\r\n}\r\n.help-block {\r\n    display: block;\r\n    margin-bottom: 9px;\r\n}\r\n.help-inline {\r\n    display: inline-block;\r\n    *display: inline;\r\n    *zoom: 1;\r\n    vertical-align: middle;\r\n    padding-left: 5px;\r\n}\r\n.form-horizontal input,\r\n.form-horizontal .help-inline {\r\n    display: inline-block;\r\n    margin-bottom: 0;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.control-group {\r\n    margin-bottom: 9px;\r\n}\r\n.form-horizontal .control-group {\r\n    margin-bottom: 18px;\r\n    *zoom: 1;\r\n}\r\n.form-horizontal .control-group:before,\r\n.form-horizontal .control-group:after {\r\n    display: table;\r\n    content: \"\";\r\n}\r\n.form-horizontal .control-group:after {\r\n    clear: both;\r\n}\r\n.form-horizontal .control-label {\r\n    float: left;\r\n    width: 140px;\r\n    padding-top: 5px;\r\n    text-align: right;\r\n}\r\n.form-horizontal .controls {\r\n    margin-left: 160px;\r\n    *display: inline-block;\r\n    *margin-left: 0;\r\n    *padding-left: 20px;\r\n}\r\n.form-horizontal .help-block {\r\n    margin-top: 9px;\r\n    margin-bottom: 0;\r\n}\r\n.form-horizontal .form-actions {\r\n    padding-left: 160px;\r\n}\r\n/*helps info*/\r\n\r\n.form-horizontal .help-inline {\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    padding: 3px 6px;\r\n    background: #444;\r\n    color: #fff;\r\n    z-index: -2;\r\n    border-radius: 3px;\r\n    -webkit-transition:all 0.5s;\r\n    -moz-transition:all 0.5s;\r\n    -o-transition:all 0.5s;\r\n    -ms-transition:all 0.5s;\r\n    transition:all 0.5s;\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    margin-left: -500px;\r\n}\t\r\n.form-horizontal .help-inline::before {\r\n    content:\"\";\r\n    display: block;\r\n    height: 0;\r\n    width: 0;\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    top: 7px;\r\n    left: -12px;\r\n    border: 6px solid transparent;\r\n    border-right-color: #444;\r\n    z-index: 2;\r\n}\r\n.controls {\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n}\t\r\n.form-horizontal .help-block {\r\n    background: #444;\r\n    border-radius: 3px;\r\n    padding: 3px 6px;\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    top: 28px;\r\n    left: 0;\r\n    z-index: -2;\r\n    color: #fff;\r\n    -webkit-transition:all 0.5s;\r\n    -moz-transition:all 0.5s;\r\n    -o-transition:all 0.5s;\r\n    -ms-transition:all 0.5s;\r\n    transition:all 0.5s;\r\n}\r\n.form-horizontal .help-block::after {\r\n    border: 6px solid transparent;\r\n    border-bottom-color: #444;\r\n    content:\"\";\r\n    display: block;\r\n    height:0;\r\n    width: 0;\r\n    left: 5px;\r\n    top: -12px;\r\n    z-index: 2;\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n} \r\n.form-horizontal input:active + .help-inline,\r\n.form-horizontal input:focus + .help-inline {\r\n    margin-left: 8px;\r\n}\r\n.form-horizontal .controls-block input:active,\r\n.form-horizontal .controls-block input:focus {\r\n    margin-bottom: 35px;\r\n}','','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js','CSS 示例-CSS3 实现 tips',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',2,NULL,'2013-11-21 14:13:33',NULL,NULL,'','');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (127,'<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../style/style.css\" />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <div class=\"tips tips-left\"></div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"tips tips-top\"></div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"tips tips-right\"></div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"tips tips-bottom\"></div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"tips tips-top tips-succ\"></div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"tips tips-top tips-error\"></div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"tips tips-top tips-focus\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    height: 800px;\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.tips{\r\n    float: left;\r\n    position: relative !important;\r\n        \r\n    height: 100px;\r\n    width: 200px;\r\n        \r\n    margin: 30px;\r\n}','','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js','CSS 示例-CSS 实现 tips 提示信息',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',4,NULL,'2013-11-29 10:43:57',NULL,NULL,'48,4','原创,UI');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (128,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>CSS 实现分别引导效果</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <span class=\"track track-first\">第一步</span>\r\n    <span class=\"track track-on\">第二步</span>\r\n    <span class=\"track\">第三步</span>\r\n    <span class=\"track track-last\">第四步</span>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}','','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../style/style.css','CSS 示例-CSS 实现分步引导',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',4,NULL,'2013-11-29 12:22:50',NULL,NULL,'48,4','原创,UI');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (129,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>WebGL 实验-1</h3>\r\n    \r\n<!-- \r\n    参考教程\r\n    http://www.web-tinker.com/article/20158.html\r\n    http://www.cnblogs.com/jz1108/archive/2011/09/08/2149827.html\r\n-->\r\n    \r\n    <p>WebGL 流程：\r\n        <br />1. 从 canvas 对象中获取 WebGL 上下文\r\n        <br />2. 设置视口\r\n        <br />3. 设置 Buffer、ArrayBuffer 和类型化数组\r\n        <br />4. 设置着色器\r\n        <br />5. 绘制图元\r\n        <br />\r\n        <br />参考教程\r\n        <br /><a href=\"http://www.web-tinker.com/article/20158.html\">\r\n            http://www.web-tinker.com/article/20158.html\r\n        </a>\r\n        <br /><a href=\"http://www.web-tinker.com/article/20159.html\">\r\n            http://www.web-tinker.com/article/20159.html\r\n        </a>\r\n        <br /><a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/jz1108/archive/2011/09/08/2149827.html\">\r\n            http://www.cnblogs.com/jz1108/archive/2011/09/08/2149827.html\r\n        </a>\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n    <canvas id=\"canvas3D\" width=\"600\" height=\"300\">\r\n        如果您看到这段文字，说明您的浏览器不支持 WebGL，请更新浏览器\r\n    </canvas>    \r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var canvas = $(\'#canvas3D\').get(0),\r\n        w = canvas.width, h = canvas.height,\r\n        gl = null,\r\n        vertexBuffer,\r\n        verts = [    // 坐标点 数组\r\n            0, 1, 0,\r\n            -0.9, -0.9 ,0,\r\n            0.9, -0.9, 0,\r\n            0.5, 0.5, 0,\r\n            -0.8, 0.5, 0,\r\n            0.3, -0.5, 0,\r\n            -0.5, -0.5, 0,\r\n            0.1, 0.2, 0,\r\n            0.8, -0.8, -1,\r\n            0, 0.9, 1,\r\n            -1, 0, 1\r\n        ],        \r\n        verSize = 3,    // 每组坐标点的数据个数\r\n        nVerts = Math.floor( verts.length / verSize ),\r\n        shaderProgram,\r\n        vertexShader,\r\n        vertexShaderSource = \'attribute vec4 vertexPos;\' +\r\n            \'void main(void){gl_Position = vertexPos;}\',\r\n        fragmentShader,\r\n        // 设置颜色\r\n        fragmentShaderSource = \r\n            \'void main(void){gl_FragColor = vec4(1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1);}\',\r\n        shaderVertexPositionAttribute\r\n        ;\r\n    \r\n    if( \'getContext\' in canvas ){\r\n        gl = canvas.getContext(\'experimental-webgl\');\r\n    }\r\n    if( !gl ){\r\n        alert(\'您的浏览器不支持 WebGL，请更新！\');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    // 设置 WebGL 视口\r\n    gl.viewport(0, 0, w, h);\r\n    \r\n    // 创建程序（仅仅是创建而已。。。）\r\n    shaderProgram = gl.createProgram();\r\n    \r\n    // 创建顶点着色器和片段着色器\r\n    vertexShader = gl.createShader( gl.VERTEX_SHADER );\r\n    fragmentShader = gl.createShader( gl.FRAGMENT_SHADER );\r\n    \r\n    // 把源码添加进着色器\r\n    gl.shaderSource(vertexShader, vertexShaderSource);\r\n    gl.shaderSource(fragmentShader, fragmentShaderSource);\r\n    \r\n    // 编译着色器\r\n    gl.compileShader( vertexShader );\r\n    gl.compileShader( fragmentShader );\r\n    \r\n    // 把着色器添加到程序中\r\n    gl.attachShader(shaderProgram, vertexShader);\r\n    gl.attachShader(shaderProgram, fragmentShader);\r\n    \r\n    // 把两个着色器程序链接成一个完整的程序\r\n    gl.linkProgram( shaderProgram );\r\n\r\n    // 在显存中建立数据缓冲区\r\n    vertexBuffer = gl.createBuffer();\r\n    \r\n    // 设置数据缓冲区为当前操作对象\r\n    gl.bindBuffer(gl.ARRAY_BUFFER, vertexBuffer);\r\n    gl.bufferData(gl.ARRAY_BUFFER, new Float32Array( verts ), gl.STATIC_DRAW);\r\n    \r\n    // 获取 顶点数据源 接口 vertexPos 的序号\r\n    shaderVertexPositionAttribute = gl.getAttribLocation(shaderProgram, \'vertexPos\');\r\n    \r\n    // 开启数组模式\r\n    gl.enableVertexAttribArray( shaderVertexPositionAttribute );\r\n    \r\n    // 用黑色清空背景\r\n    gl.clearColor(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0);\r\n    gl.clear( gl.COLOR_BUFFER_BIT );\r\n    \r\n    // 设置顶点数组\r\n    gl.bindBuffer(gl.ARRAY_BUFFER, vertexBuffer);\r\n    \r\n    // 设置着色器 把程序放入显存中\r\n    gl.useProgram( shaderProgram );\r\n    \r\n    // 设置着色器参数：点点坐标、投影矩阵和模型视图矩阵\r\n    gl.vertexAttribPointer(shaderVertexPositionAttribute, verSize, gl.FLOAT,\r\n                          false, 0, 0);\r\n    \r\n    // 绘制物体\r\n    gl.drawArrays(gl.LINE_LOOP, 0, nVerts);\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js','WebGL 实验-1',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',3,NULL,'2013-11-29 17:52:12',NULL,NULL,'92,3,137','WebGL,HTML5,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (130,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>WebGL 实验-2 使用 three.js</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <p>\r\n        目前的 3D 世界当中至少包括以下几点基础的东西\r\n        <br />1. 一个场景\r\n        <br />2. 一个渲染器\r\n        <br />3. 一个摄像机\r\n        <br />4. 一个对象或者至少两个材质\r\n    </p>\r\n    \r\n    <div id=\"testTarget\" class=\"testTarget\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.testTarget{\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n    width: 500px;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var target = $(\'#testTarget\')[0],\r\n        renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer({\r\n            antialias: true\r\n        }),    // 创建 Three.js 渲染器，并添加到目标容器中\r\n        scene = new THREE.Scene(),    // 创建 Three.js 场景\r\n        camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera(45,\r\n                                             target.offsetWidth / target.offsetHeight,\r\n                                             1, 4000),    // 创建相机，并添加到场景中\r\n        \r\n        light = new THREE.DirectionalLight(0xffffff, 2.5),// 创建一个平行光光源照射到物体上\r\n        \r\n        // 创建一个接受光照并带有纹理映射的立方体，并添加到场景中\r\n        mapUrl = \'../image/demo/demoImage-5.jpg\',\r\n        map = THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture( mapUrl ),    // 一个带纹理映射的立方体\r\n        material = new THREE.MeshPhongMaterial({\r\n            map: map\r\n        }),    // 创建一个 Phong 材质来处理着色，并传递给纹理映射\r\n        \r\n        geometry = new THREE.CubeGeometry(1, 1, 1),    // 创建一个立方体的几何体\r\n        cube = new THREE.Mesh(geometry, material),        // 将几何体和材质放到一个网格中\r\n        mesh,\r\n        animating = false,\r\n        run = function(){\r\n            // 渲染绘制\r\n            renderer.render(scene, camera);\r\n            \r\n            if( animating ){\r\n                cube.rotation.x -= 0.01;\r\n                cube.rotation.y -= 0.01;\r\n            }\r\n            \r\n            requestAnimationFrame( run );\r\n        };\r\n        \r\n// 设置场景 将 dom 对象添加到页面中\r\n    renderer.setSize(target.offsetWidth, target.offsetHeight);\r\n    \r\n    target.appendChild( renderer.domElement );\r\n    \r\n/*    \r\n    // 创建一个矩形几何体，并添加到场景中\r\n    geometry = new THREE.PlaneGeometry(1, 1);    // 创建矩形\r\n    \r\n    mesh = new THREE.Mesh(geometry, new THREE.MeshBasicMaterial());\r\n    \r\n    scene.add( mesh );\r\n*/\r\n    \r\n// 设置摄像头 添加到场景    \r\n    camera.position.set(0, 0, 3);    // 相机距离原点的位置 x, y, z\r\n    \r\n    scene.add( camera );\r\n    \r\n// 设置光线 添加到场景\r\n    light.position.set(0, 0, 1);\r\n    \r\n    scene.add( light );\r\n     \r\n// 设置网格在场景中的朝向，否则将不会看到立方体的形状\r\n    cube.rotation.x = Math.PI /5;\r\n    cube.rotation.y = Math.PI /5;\r\n    \r\n    scene.add( cube );    // 将立方体网格添加到场景中\r\n    \r\n    // 绑定事件\r\n    $(renderer.domElement).on(\'click\', function(e){\r\n        e.preventDefault();\r\n        \r\n        animating = !animating;\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n// 动画渲染\r\n    run();\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/three/three.min.js','WebGL 实验-2 使用 three.js',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',3,NULL,'2013-11-30 17:34:42',NULL,NULL,'92,99,3,137','WebGL,three.js,HTML5,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (131,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>WebGL 实验-3 构建地球</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <div id=\"testTarget\" class=\"testTarget\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.testTarget{\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n    width: 500px;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var target = $(\'#testTarget\')[0],\r\n        renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer({\r\n            antialias: true\r\n        }),    // 渲染器\r\n        \r\n        scene = new THREE.Scene(),    // 场景\r\n        \r\n        light = new THREE.PointLight(0xffffff, 2, 100),    // 光照 点光源\r\n        camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera(45, target.offsetWidth / target.offsetHeight, 1, 4000),    // 摄像机\r\n                \r\n        // 加载图片\r\n        earthMap = THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture( \'../image/demo/earth_atmos_2048.jpg\' ),    // 纹理图片路径\r\n        material = new THREE.MeshPhongMaterial({map: earthMap}),    // 纹理\r\n        geometry = new THREE.SphereGeometry(1, 32, 32),    // 球形 第二和第三个参数是告诉要用多少个交叉区域组成球体表面以及每个交叉区域中包含多少个三角形\r\n        mesh = new THREE.Mesh(geometry, material),\r\n        \r\n        rotationY = 0.001,\r\n        rotationZ = -0.41,\r\n        \r\n        animating = true,\r\n        animateId = null,\r\n        run = function(){\r\n            // 渲染绘制\r\n            renderer.render(scene, camera);\r\n            \r\n            // 下次渲染时，改变 Y 轴旋转，以造成动画效果\r\n            mesh.rotation.y += rotationY;\r\n                         \r\n            animateId = requestAnimationFrame( run );\r\n        };\r\n    \r\n    renderer.setSize(target.offsetWidth, target.offsetHeight);\r\n    \r\n    target.appendChild( renderer.domElement );\r\n    \r\n    $(renderer.domElement).on(\'click\', function(e){\r\n        e.preventDefault();\r\n       \r\n        animating = !animating;\r\n        \r\n        if( animating ){\r\n            animateId = requestAnimationFrame( run );\r\n        }\r\n        else{\r\n            animateId && cancelAnimationFrame( animateId );\r\n            animateId = null;\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    mesh.rotation.y = Math.PI/6 *5;\r\n    mesh.rotation.z = rotationZ;\r\n\r\n    scene.add( mesh );\r\n    \r\n    light.position.set(-10, 0, 20);\r\n    \r\n    scene.add( light );\r\n    \r\n    camera.position.set(0, 0, 3);\r\n        \r\n    run();\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/three/three.min.js','WebGL 实验-3 构建地球',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',3,NULL,'2013-12-02 18:28:10',NULL,NULL,'92,99,3,137','WebGL,three.js,HTML5,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (132,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>WebGL 实验-4 地球与月球</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <div id=\"testTarget\" class=\"testTarget\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.testTarget{\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n    width: 500px;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var target = $(\'#testTarget\')[0],\r\n        renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer({\r\n            antialias: true\r\n        }),    // 渲染器\r\n        \r\n        scene = new THREE.Scene(),    // 场景\r\n        \r\n        light = new THREE.PointLight(0xffffff, 2, 100),    // 光照\r\n        camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera(70, target.offsetWidth / target.offsetHeight, 1, 4000),    // 摄像机\r\n        \r\n        earthGroup = new THREE.Object3D(),    // 创建一个包含地球和云层的群组\r\n        \r\n        // 加载图片\r\n        earthMap = THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture( \'../image/demo/earth_atmos_2048.jpg\' ),    // 纹理图片路径\r\n        normalMap = THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture( \'../image/demo/earth_normal_2048.jpg\' ),    // 高度图的法线贴图\r\n        specularMap = THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture( \'../image/demo/earth_specular_2048.jpg\' ),    // 高亮贴图\r\n                \r\n        shader = THREE.ShaderLib[\'normalmap\'],    // 原 demo 为 THREE.ShaderUtils.lib[\'normal\']，可能为版本问题\r\n        uniforms = THREE.UniformsUtils.clone( shader.uniforms ),\r\n        shaderMaterial,    // 自定义着色器\r\n        \r\n        globeGeometry = new THREE.SphereGeometry(1, 32, 32),    // 球形\r\n        globeMesh,\r\n        \r\n        // 创建云层\r\n        cloudsMap = THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture( \'../image/demo/earth_clouds_1024.png\' ),    // 云层贴图\r\n        cloudsMaterial = new THREE.MeshLambertMaterial({\r\n            color: 0xffffff,\r\n            map: cloudsMap,\r\n            transparent: true\r\n        }),    // 在 Lambert 着色法中，无论观察者的角度如何变化，物体表面上的明亮程度都一样\r\n        cloudsGeometry = new THREE.SphereGeometry(1.005, 32, 32),\r\n        cloudsMesh = new THREE.Mesh(cloudsGeometry, cloudsMaterial),\r\n        \r\n        // 创建月球\r\n        moonGroup = new THREE.Object3D(),\r\n        \r\n        moonMap = THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture( \'../image/demo/moon_1024.jpg\' ),    // 月球图层\r\n        moonGeometry = new THREE.SphereGeometry(1/3.7*1.2, 32, 32),\r\n        moonMaterial = new THREE.MeshPhongMaterial({\r\n            map: moonMap,\r\n            ambient: 0x888888\r\n        }),\r\n        moonMesh = new THREE.Mesh(moonGeometry, moonMaterial),\r\n\r\n        rotationY = 0.001,\r\n        rotationZ = -0.41,\r\n        \r\n        animating = true,\r\n        animateId = null,\r\n        run = function(){\r\n            // 渲染绘制\r\n            renderer.render(scene, camera);\r\n                \r\n            globeMesh.rotation.y += rotationY *10;\r\n            cloudsMesh.rotation.y += rotationY *0.95 *10;\r\n            moonGroup.rotation.y += rotationY /28 *10;\r\n            \r\n            animateId = requestAnimationFrame( run );\r\n        };\r\n    \r\n    renderer.setSize(target.offsetWidth, target.offsetHeight);\r\n    \r\n    target.appendChild( renderer.domElement );\r\n    \r\n    $(renderer.domElement).on(\'click\', function(e){\r\n        e.preventDefault();\r\n        \r\n        animating = !animating;\r\n        \r\n        if( animating ){\r\n            animateId = requestAnimationFrame( run );\r\n        }\r\n        else{\r\n            animateId && cancelAnimationFrame( animateId );\r\n            animateId = null;\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    uniforms[\'tNormal\'].value = normalMap;    // 法线纹理    原 demo 属性为 texture，可能因为版本问题\r\n    uniforms[\'tDiffuse\'].value = earthMap;    // 漫反射纹理    原 demo 属性为 texture，可能因为版本问题\r\n    uniforms[\'tSpecular\'].value = specularMap;    // 高光纹理    原 demo 属性为 texture，可能因为版本问题\r\n    \r\n    uniforms[ \"enableDiffuse\" ].value = true;\r\n    uniforms[ \"enableSpecular\" ].value = true;\r\n    \r\n/*\r\n    uniforms[ \"enableAO\" ].value = false;\r\n    uniforms[ \"uDiffuseColor\" ].value.setHex( 0xffffff );    // 漫反射颜色\r\n    uniforms[ \"uSpecularColor\" ].value.setHex( 0x333333 );    // 高光颜色\r\n    uniforms[ \"uAmbientColor\" ].value.setHex( 0x000000 );    // 环境光颜色\r\n    uniforms[ \"uShininess\" ].value = 15;    // 物体表面光滑度\r\n */\r\n    shaderMaterial = new THREE.ShaderMaterial({\r\n        fragmentShader: shader.fragmentShader,\r\n        vertexShader: shader.vertexShader,\r\n        uniforms: uniforms,\r\n        lights: true\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    globeGeometry.computeTangents();    // 为着色器计算切线\r\n\r\n    globeMesh = new THREE.Mesh(globeGeometry, shaderMaterial);\r\n\r\n    globeMesh.rotation.z = rotationZ;    // 倾斜地球\r\n\r\n    earthGroup.add( globeMesh );\r\n\r\n    cloudsMesh.rotation.z = rotationZ;\r\n\r\n    earthGroup.add( cloudsMesh );\r\n  \r\n    moonMesh.position.set(Math.sqrt(356400/6371/2), 0, -Math.sqrt(356400/6371/2));\r\n    moonMesh.rotation.y = Math.PI;    // 旋转月球，让它一个面始终朝向地球\r\n\r\n    moonGroup.add( moonMesh );\r\n    moonGroup.rotation.x = 0.089;\r\n    \r\n    earthGroup.add( moonGroup );\r\n    \r\n    scene.add( earthGroup );\r\n    \r\n    light.position.set(-10, 0, 20);\r\n    \r\n    scene.add( light );\r\n    \r\n    camera.position.set(0, 0, 3);\r\n    \r\n    run();\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/three/three.min.js','WebGL 实验-4 地球与月球',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',3,NULL,'2013-12-06 15:14:20',NULL,NULL,'92,99,3,137','WebGL,three.js,HTML5,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (133,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>WebGL 实验-5 粒子系统</h3>\r\n    <div id=\"testTarget\" class=\"testTarget\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n.testTarget{\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n    width: 500px;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n/*\r\n    var rings = function(innerRadius, outerRadius, nSegments){\r\n        \r\n            outerRadius = outerRadius || 1;\r\n            innerRadius = innerRadius || 0.5;\r\n            nSegments = nSegments || 10;\r\n            \r\n            var rings = new THREE.Geometry();\r\n                i = 0, j,\r\n                twopi = Math.PI *2,\r\n                iVer = Math.max(2, nSegments),\r\n                origin = new THREE.Vector3(0, 0, 0),\r\n                \r\n                fRad1, fRad2,\r\n                fx1, fy1,\r\n                fx2, fy2,\r\n                fx3, fy3,\r\n                fx4, fy4;\r\n            \r\n            for(j = iVer + 1; i < j; i++){\r\n                fRad1 = i / iVer * twopi;\r\n                fRad2 = (i +1) / iVer * twopi;\r\n                fx1 = innerRadius * Math.cos( fRad1 );\r\n                fy1 = innerRadius * Math.sin( fRad1 );\r\n                fx2 = outerRadius * Math.cos( fRad1 );\r\n                fy2 = outerRadius * Math.sin( fRad1 );\r\n                fx3 = outerRadius * Math.cos( fRad2 );\r\n                fy3 = outerRadius * Math.sin( fRad2 );\r\n                fx4 = innerRadius * Math.cos( fRad2 );\r\n                fy4 = innerRadius * Math.sin( fRad2 );\r\n                \r\n                rings.vertices.push(new THREE.Vertex( new THREE.Vertor3(fx1, fy1, 0) ),\r\n                                      new THREE.Vertex( new THREE.Vertor3(fx2, fy2, 0) ),\r\n                                      new THREE.Vertex( new THREE.Vertor3(fx3, fy3, 0) ),\r\n                                      new THREE.Vertex( new THREE.Vertor3(fx4, fy4, 0) ));\r\n            }\r\n            \r\n            for(i = 0; i < iVer; i++){\r\n                rings.faces.push(new THREE.Face3(i *4, i *4+1, i *4+2),\r\n                           new THREE.Face3(i *4, i *4+2, i *4+3));\r\n                \r\n                rings.faceVertexUvs[0].push([\r\n                    new THREE.UV(0, 1),\r\n                    new THREE.UV(1, 1),\r\n                    new THREE.UV(1, 0)\r\n                ], [\r\n                    new THREE.UV(0, 1),\r\n                    new THREE.UV(1, 0),\r\n                    new THREE.UV(0, 0)\r\n                    // UV 坐标，定义了纹理图片的每个像素如何映射到网格表面，取值范围通常是 0 到 1\r\n                    // U 轴代表水平方向，向右递增\r\n                    // V 轴代表垂直方向，向上递增\r\n                ]);\r\n            }\r\n                        \r\n            rings.computeCentroids();\r\n            rings.computeFaceNormals();\r\n            \r\n            rings.boundingSphere = {\r\n                radius: outerRadius\r\n            };    // 提供一些用于拾取和剪裁所需的数据\r\n            \r\n            return rings;\r\n        };\r\n */\r\n\r\n    var target = $(\'#testTarget\')[0],\r\n        renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer({\r\n            antialias: true\r\n        }),    // 渲染器\r\n        scene = new THREE.Scene(),    // 场景\r\n        \r\n        camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera(45, target.offsetWidth / target.offsetHeight, 1, 4000),    // 摄像\r\n        stars = function( distance ){\r\n            var starsGroup = new THREE.Object3D(),\r\n                starsGeometry = new THREE.Geometry(),\r\n                \r\n                tempVector,\r\n                numVertices = 667,\r\n                \r\n                numMaterials = 8,\r\n                starsMaterial = [],\r\n                \r\n                numParticleSystem = 24,\r\n                \r\n                star, i;\r\n            \r\n            for(i = 0; i < numVertices; i++){\r\n                tempVector = new THREE.Vector3((Math.random() *2-1)* distance,\r\n                                               (Math.random() *2-1)* distance,\r\n                                               (Math.random() *2-1)* distance);\r\n                \r\n                if( tempVector.length() < distance ){\r\n                    tempVector = tempVector.setLength( distance );\r\n                }\r\n                \r\n                starsGeometry.vertices.push( tempVector )// new THREE.Vector3( tempVector ) );\r\n            }\r\n            \r\n            for(i = 0; i < numMaterials; i++){\r\n                starsMaterial.push( new THREE.ParticleBasicMaterial({    // 定义粒子系统的点的尺寸和颜色\r\n                    color: 0x101010 * (i +1),\r\n                    size: i %2+1,\r\n                    sizeAttenuation: false    // 在相机移动是不必重新缩放每个粒子\r\n                }));\r\n            }\r\n            \r\n            for(i = 0; i < numParticleSystem; i++){\r\n                star = new THREE.ParticleSystem(starsGeometry, starsMaterial[ i % numMaterials ]);\r\n                star.rotation.y = i /(Math.PI *2);\r\n                \r\n                starsGroup.add( star );\r\n            }\r\n            \r\n            return starsGroup;\r\n        },\r\n        orbit = function( distance ){\r\n            var geometry = new THREE.Geometry(),\r\n                material = new THREE.LineBasicMaterial({    // 线条材质\r\n                    color: 0xffffff,\r\n                    opacity: 0.5,\r\n                    lineWidth: 2\r\n                }),\r\n                line,\r\n                tempVector,\r\n                numSegments = 120,\r\n                len = 60, twopi = 2 * Math.PI,\r\n                i, j;\r\n            \r\n            for(i = 0, j = numSegments +1; i < j; i++){\r\n                tempVector = new THREE.Vector3(distance * Math.cos( i / numSegments * twopi ), 0, distance * Math.sin( i / numSegments * twopi ));\r\n                \r\n                geometry.vertices.push( tempVector );\r\n            }\r\n            \r\n            line = new THREE.Line(geometry, material);\r\n            line.rotation.x = Math.PI /2;\r\n            \r\n            return line;\r\n        };\r\n    \r\n    renderer.setSize(target.offsetWidth, target.offsetHeight);\r\n    \r\n    target.appendChild( renderer.domElement );\r\n    \r\n    scene.add( stars( 3960 ) );\r\n    \r\n    scene.add( orbit( 1 ) );\r\n    \r\n    camera.position.set(0, 0, 3);\r\n    \r\n    renderer.render(scene, camera);\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/three/three.min.js','WebGL 实验-5 粒子系统',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',3,NULL,'2013-12-06 19:04:36',NULL,NULL,'92,99,3,137','WebGL,three.js,HTML5,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (134,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3></h3>\r\n    \r\n    <div id=\"testTarget\" class=\"testTarget\"></div>\r\n    \r\n    <script id=\"fragmentShader\" type=\"x-shader/x-fragment\">\r\n        uniform float time;\r\n        \r\n        uniform sampler2D texture1;\r\n        uniform sampler2D texture2;\r\n        \r\n        varying vec2 texCoord;\r\n        \r\n        void main( void ){\r\n            vec4 noise = texture2D(texture1, texCoord);\r\n            \r\n            vec2 T1 = texCoord + vec2(1.5, -1.5) * time *0.01;\r\n            vec2 T2 = texCoord + vec2(-0.5, 2.0) * time *0.01;\r\n            \r\n            T1.x -= noise.r *2.0;\r\n            T1.y += noise.g *4.0;\r\n            T2.x += noise.g *2.0;\r\n            T2.y += noise.b *0.2;\r\n            \r\n            float p = texture2D(texture1, T1 *2.0).a +0.25;\r\n            \r\n            vec4 color = texture2D(texture2, T2);\r\n            vec4 temp = color *2.0 * ( vec4(p, p, p, p) ) + ( color * color );\r\n            gl_FragColor = temp;\r\n        }\r\n    </script>\r\n    \r\n    <script id=\"vertexShader\" type=\"x-shader/x-vertex\">\r\n        varying vec2 texCoord;\r\n        \r\n        void main(){\r\n            texCoord = uv;\r\n            vec4 mvPosition = modelViewMatrix * vec4(position, 1.0);\r\n            gl_Position = projectionMatrix * mvPosition;\r\n        }\r\n    </script>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n.testTarget{\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n    width: 500px;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var target = $(\'#testTarget\')[0],\r\n        renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer({\r\n            antialias: true\r\n        }),    // 渲染器\r\n        \r\n        scene = new THREE.Scene(),    // 场景\r\n        light = new THREE.PointLight(0xffffff, 1.2, 100000),    // 光照 点光源\r\n        camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera(45, target.offsetWidth / target.offsetHeight, 1, 4000),    // 摄像机\r\n\r\n        sunGroup = new THREE.Object3D(),\r\n        sunUniforms = {\r\n            time: {\r\n                type: \'f\',\r\n                value: 1.0\r\n            },\r\n            texture1: {\r\n                type: \'t\',\r\n                value: THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture(\'../image/demo/cloud.png\')\r\n                /* 原 demo 属性值为\r\n                type: \'t\',\r\n                value: 0,\r\n                texture: THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture(\'../image/demo/cloud.png\')\r\n                 */\r\n            },\r\n            texture2: {\r\n                type: \'t\',\r\n                value: THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture(\'../image/demo/lavatile.jpg\')\r\n                /* 原 demo 属性值为\r\n                type: \'t\',\r\n                value: 1,\r\n                texture: THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture(\'../image/demo/lavatile.png\')\r\n                 */\r\n            }\r\n        },\r\n        sunMaterial,\r\n        sunGeometry = new THREE.SphereGeometry(1, 64, 64),\r\n        sunMesh,\r\n        \r\n        clock = new THREE.Clock(),\r\n        animating = true,\r\n        animateId = null,\r\n        run = function(){\r\n            renderer.render(scene, camera);\r\n            \r\n            var delta = clock.getDelta();\r\n            \r\n            sunUniforms.time.value += delta;\r\n            \r\n            sunGroup.rotation.y -= 0.001;\r\n            \r\n            animateId = requestAnimationFrame( run );\r\n        };\r\n\r\n    renderer.setSize(target.offsetWidth, target.offsetHeight);\r\n    \r\n    target.appendChild( renderer.domElement );\r\n    \r\n    sunUniforms.texture1.value.wrapS = sunUniforms.texture1.value.wrapT = THREE.RepeatWrapping;\r\n    sunUniforms.texture2.value.wrapS = sunUniforms.texture2.value.wrapT = THREE.RepeatWrapping;\r\n/* 原 demo 属性值为\r\n    sunUniforms.texture1.texture.wrapS = sunUniforms.texture1.texture.wrapT = THREE.RepeatWrapping;\r\n    sunUniforms.texture2.texture.wrapS = sunUniforms.texture2.texture.wrapT = THREE.RepeatWrapping;             \r\n */\r\n    \r\n    sunMaterial = new THREE.ShaderMaterial({\r\n        uniforms: sunUniforms,\r\n        vertexShader: $(\'#vertexShader\').text(),\r\n        fragmentShader: $(\'#fragmentShader\').text()\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    sunMesh = new THREE.Mesh(sunGeometry, sunMaterial);\r\n    \r\n    sunGroup.add( sunMesh );\r\n    sunGroup.add( light );\r\n    \r\n    scene.add( sunGroup );\r\n    \r\n    camera.position.set(0, 0, 3);\r\n    \r\n    $(renderer.domElement).on(\'click\', function(e){\r\n        e.preventDefault();\r\n       \r\n        animating = !animating;\r\n        \r\n        if( animating ){\r\n            animateId = requestAnimationFrame( run );\r\n        }\r\n        else{\r\n            animateId && cancelAnimationFrame( animateId );\r\n            animateId = null;\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    run();\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/three/three.min.js','WebGL 实验-6 构建太阳',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',3,NULL,'2013-12-09 16:26:45',NULL,NULL,'92,99,3,137','WebGL,three.js,HTML5,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (135,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>jQuery UI 日期选择器 Datepicker</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <input type=\"text\" name=\"date\" id=\"datePicker\" />\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var now = new Date();\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#datePicker\').datepicker({\r\n        changeMonth: true,    // 以下拉列表来选择月份\r\n        changeYear: true,    // 以下拉列表来选择年份\r\n        dateFormat: \'yy-mm-dd\',    // 输出的时间格式\r\n        dayNames: [\r\n            \'星期日\', \'星期一\', \'星期二\', \'星期三\', \'星期四\', \'星期五\', \'星期六\'\r\n        ],\r\n        dayNamesMin: [\r\n            \'日\', \'一\', \'二\', \'三\', \'四\', \'五\', \'六\'\r\n        ],\r\n        firstDay: 1,    // 每周以哪天开始\r\n        monthNames: [\r\n            \'一月\', \'二月\', \'三月\',\r\n            \'四月\', \'五月\', \'六月\',\r\n            \'七月\', \'八月\', \'九月\',\r\n            \'十月\', \'十一月\', \'十二月\'\r\n        ],\r\n        monthNamesShort: [\r\n            \'一月\', \'二月\', \'三月\',\r\n            \'四月\', \'五月\', \'六月\',\r\n            \'七月\', \'八月\', \'九月\',\r\n            \'十月\', \'十一月\', \'十二月\'\r\n        ],\r\n        numberOfMonths: [1, 2],    // 显示月份的数量 行数 每行个数\r\n        \r\n        beforeShowDay: $.datepicker.noWeekends,    // 周末不可选\r\n        showMonthAfterYear: true,    // 在年之后显示月份\r\n        showOtherMonths: true,    // 显示前后月份的日期\r\n        showWeek: true,    // 显示第几周\r\n        weekHeader: \'周\',    // 显示第几周的表头的文字\r\n        yearRange: \'2002:\'+ (now.getFullYear()+1),    // 年选择的区间\r\n        \r\n        showButtonPanel: true    // 底部操作按钮\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n   //alert( $.datepicker.formatDate( \'yy-mm-dd\', new Date( 2007, 1 - 1, 26 ) ) );\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.css,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.js','jQuery UI-日期选择器 Datepicker',NULL,'../image/preview/jQueryUI_datepicker.jpg',1,NULL,'2013-12-10 10:54:09',NULL,NULL,'10,96,4,137','jQuery,jQuery UI,UI,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (136,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>jQuery UI-拖拽功能 Draggable &amp; Droppable</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <input type=\"button\" id=\"drag\" class=\"btn\" value=\"开始拖拽\" />\r\n    <div id=\"dragBox\" class=\"dragBox\"></div>\r\n    \r\n    <div id=\"dropBox\" class=\"dropBox\">绿色的方块可以被拖到这个方块中</div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n.btn{\r\n    clear: both;\r\n    float: left;\r\n    z-index: 10;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.dragBox{\r\n    float: left;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n    width: 200px;\r\n    \r\n    padding: 20px;\r\n    background: lime;\r\n    color: #fff;\r\n    font-size: 20px;\r\n    font-weight: bolder;\r\n    line-height: 200%;\r\n}\r\n.dropBox{\r\n    float: left;\r\n\r\n    height: 300px;\r\n    width: 300px;\r\n    \r\n    padding: 20px;\r\n    background: #efefef;\r\n    \r\n    color: #fff;\r\n    font-size: 20px;\r\n    font-weight: bolder;\r\n    line-height: 200%;\r\n}\r\n.yellow{\r\n    background: yellow;\r\n    color: #000;\r\n}\r\n.red{\r\n    background: red;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var $dragBox = $(\'#dragBox\').draggable({\r\n            containment: \'parent\',\r\n        }).draggable(\'disable\'),\r\n        $dropBox = $(\'#dropBox\').droppable({\r\n            drop: function(e, ui) {\r\n                $(this).addClass(\'yellow\').removeClass(\'red\').html(\'现在绿色方块被拖入这个方块中了！\');\r\n            },\r\n            out: function(e, ui) {\r\n                $(this).removeClass(\'yellow\').addClass(\'red\').html(\'现在绿色方块被拖出这个方块了！\');\r\n            }\r\n        });\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#drag\').on(\'click\', function(){\r\n        var $self = $(this);\r\n        \r\n        if( $self.data(\'drag\') ){\r\n            $self.data(\'drag\', false).val(\'开始拖拽\');\r\n            \r\n            $dragBox.html(\'这个方块现在不可以拖动了\').draggable( \"disable\" );\r\n        }\r\n        else{\r\n            $self.data(\'drag\', true).val(\'停止拖拽\');\r\n            \r\n            $dragBox.html(\'这个方块现在可以拖动了\').draggable(\'enable\');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.css,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.js','jQuery UI-拖拽功能 Draggable & Droppable',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',1,NULL,'2013-12-11 11:16:47',NULL,NULL,'4,96,10,137','UI,jQuery UI,jQuery,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (137,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>jQuery UI-调整大小 Resizable</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <input type=\"button\" value=\"开始调整\" id=\"resize\" class=\"resize\" />\r\n    <div id=\"resizeBox\" class=\"resizeBox\">\r\n        这个方块初始为 200px * 200px\r\n        \r\n        <p></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.resizeBox{\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n    width: 200px;\r\n    \r\n    padding: 20px;\r\n    background: lime;\r\n    color: #fff;\r\n    font-size: 20px;\r\n    font-weight: bolder;\r\n    line-height: 200%;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var $resizeBox = $(\'#resizeBox\').resizable({\r\n        resize: function(e, ui){\r\n            var size = ui.size;\r\n            $(this).find(\'p\').html(\'现在这个方块宽度为 \'+ size.width +\'px，高度为 \'+ size.height +\'px\');\r\n        }\r\n    }).resizable(\'disable\');\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#resize\').on(\'click\', function(){\r\n        var $self = $(this);\r\n        \r\n        if( $self.data(\'resize\') ){\r\n            $self.data(\'resize\', false).val(\'开始调整\');\r\n            $resizeBox.resizable(\'disable\');\r\n        }\r\n        else{\r\n            $self.data(\'resize\', true).val(\'关闭调整\');\r\n            $resizeBox.resizable(\'enable\');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.css,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.js','jQuery UI-调整大小 Resizable',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',1,NULL,'2013-12-11 14:15:14',NULL,NULL,'96,10,4,137','jQuery UI,jQuery,UI,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (138,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>jQuery UI-选取 Selectable</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"resultArea\">\r\n        <input type=\"button\" value=\"开始选取\" id=\"select\" class=\"select btn\" />\r\n        <p id=\"selectingResult\" class=\"selectResult\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"selectedResult\" class=\"selectResult\"></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <ul id=\"selectList\" class=\"selectList\">\r\n        <li class=\"selectItem ui-widget-content\">Item 1</li>\r\n        <li class=\"selectItem ui-widget-content\">Item 2</li>\r\n        <li class=\"selectItem ui-widget-content\">Item 3</li>\r\n        <li class=\"selectItem ui-widget-content\">Item 4</li>\r\n        <li class=\"selectItem ui-widget-content\">Item 5</li>\r\n        <li class=\"selectItem ui-widget-content\">Item 6</li>\r\n        <li class=\"selectItem ui-widget-content\">Item 7</li>\r\n        <li class=\"selectItem ui-widget-content\">Item 8</li>\r\n        <li class=\"selectItem ui-widget-content\">Item 9</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.btn{\r\n    clear: both;\r\n    float: left;\r\n}\r\n.resultArea{\r\n}\r\n.selectResult{\r\n    overflow: auto;\r\n    clear: left;\r\n    height: 100px;\r\n    margin: 5px;\r\n    background: #c0c0c0;\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.selectList{\r\n    float: left;\r\n    width: 400px;\r\n    list-style: none;\r\n}\r\n.selectItem{\r\n    border: 1px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 5px;\r\n    \r\n    font-size: 20px;\r\n    line-height: 200%;\r\n    text-indent: 2em;\r\n}\r\n/* 鼠标移上时的样式 */\r\n.selectList .ui-selecting{\r\n    background: #FECA40;\r\n}\r\n/* 最终选定是的样式 */\r\n.selectList .ui-selected{\r\n    background: #F39814;\r\n    color: white;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var $selectList = $(\'#selectList\').selectable({\r\n            selecting: function(e, ui){\r\n                $selectingResult.append(\'你将选择 \'+ ui.selecting.innerHTML +\'<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                    return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                });\r\n            },\r\n            selected: function(e, ui){\r\n                $selectedResult.append(\'你最终选择了 \'+ ui.selected.innerHTML +\'<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                    return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                });\r\n            },\r\n            unselecting: function(e, ui){\r\n                $selectingResult.append(\'你将取消选择 \'+ ui.unselecting.innerHTML +\'<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                    return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                });\r\n            },\r\n            unselected: function(e, ui){\r\n                $selectedResult.append(\'你最终取消选择 \'+ ui.unselected.innerHTML +\'<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                    return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                });\r\n            }\r\n        }).selectable(\'disable\'),\r\n        $selectingResult = $(\'#selectingResult\'),\r\n        $selectedResult = $(\'#selectedResult\');\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#select\').on(\'click\', function(){\r\n        var $self = $(this);\r\n        \r\n        if( $self.data(\'select\') ){\r\n            $self.data(\'select\', false).val(\'开始选取\');\r\n            $selectList.selectable(\'disable\');\r\n        }\r\n        else{\r\n            $self.data(\'select\', true).val(\'结束选取\');\r\n            $selectList.selectable(\'enable\');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.css,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.js','jQuery UI-选取 Selectable',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',1,NULL,'2013-12-11 15:20:01',NULL,NULL,'10,4,96,137','jQuery,UI,jQuery UI,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (139,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>jQuery UI-排序 Sortable</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"resultArea\">\r\n        <input type=\"button\" value=\"开始排序\" id=\"sort\" class=\"sort btn\" />\r\n        <input type=\"button\" value=\"取消\" id=\"cancel\" class=\"sort btn\" style=\"display: none;\" />\r\n         \r\n        <p id=\"sortResult\" class=\"sortResult\"></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <ul id=\"sortList1\" class=\"sortList\">\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 1 Item 1</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 1 Item 2</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 1 Item 3</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 1 Item 4</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 1 Item 5</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 1 Item 6</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 1 Item 7</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 1 Item 8</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 1 Item 9</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    <ul id=\"sortList2\" class=\"sortList\">\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 2 Item 1</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 2 Item 2</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 2 Item 3</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 2 Item 4</li>\r\n        <li class=\"sortItem ui-state-default\">SortList 2 Item 5</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.btn{\r\n    float: left;\r\n}\r\n.resultArea{\r\n    clear: both;\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n}\r\n.sortResult{\r\n    overflow: auto;\r\n    clear: left;\r\n    height: 100px;\r\n    margin: 5px;\r\n    background: #c0c0c0;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.sortList{\r\n    float: left;\r\n    width: 40%;\r\n    margin: 0;\r\n    padding: 0;\r\n    list-style: none;\r\n}\r\n.sortItem{\r\n    border: 1px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 4%;\r\n    \r\n    cursor: pointer;\r\n    \r\n    font-size: 14px;\r\n    line-height: 40px;\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var $sortResult = $(\'#sortResult\')\r\n        , $list1 = $(\'#sortList1\').sortable({\r\n            connectWith: \'#sortList2\'    // 与列表 2 相连接\r\n            , cursor: \'move\'    // 移动时鼠标图标\r\n            , disabled: true    // 禁用\r\n            , start: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你选取了 \'+ ui.item.html() +\'<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            , stop: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你改变了 \'+ ui.item.html() +\' 的位置<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            , change: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你正在调整\'+ ui.item.html() +\' 的位置<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            , over: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你将会将 \'+ ui.item.html() +\' 移入了列表 1<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            , receive: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你将 \'+ ui.item.html() +\' 放入了列表 1<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            , remove: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你将 \'+ ui.item.html() +\' 从列表 1 移除<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n        })\r\n        , $list2 = $(\'#sortList2\').sortable({\r\n            connectWith: \'#sortList1\'    // 与列表 1 相连接\r\n            , cursor: \'move\'    // 移动时鼠标图标\r\n            , disabled: true    // 禁用\r\n            , start: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你选取了 \'+ ui.item.html() +\'<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            , stop: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你改变了 \'+ ui.item.html() +\' 的位置<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            , change: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你正在调整\'+ ui.item.html() +\' 的位置<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            , over: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你将会将 \'+ ui.item.html() +\' 移入了列表 2<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            , receive: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你将 \'+ ui.item.html() +\' 放入了列表 2<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            , remove: function(e, ui){\r\n                    $sortResult.append(\'你将 \'+ ui.item.html() +\' 从列表 2 移除<br />\').scrollTop(function(){\r\n                        return this.scrollHeight;\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            })\r\n        , sortable = false\r\n        , $cancel = $(\'#cancel\').on(\'click\', function(){\r\n            $list1.sortable(\'cancel\');\r\n            $list2.sortable(\'cancel\');\r\n        })\r\n        ;\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#sort\').on(\'click\', function(){\r\n        \r\n        if( sortable ){\r\n            this.value = \'开始排序\';\r\n            $cancel.hide();\r\n        }\r\n        else{\r\n            this.value = \'停止排序\';\r\n            $cancel.show();\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        $list1.sortable( \"enable\" );\r\n        $list2.sortable( \"enable\" );\r\n        \r\n        sortable = !sortable;\r\n    });\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.css,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.js','jQuery UI-排序 Sortable',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',1,NULL,'2013-12-11 16:32:57',NULL,NULL,'10,4,96,137','jQuery,UI,jQuery UI,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (140,'<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../script/lib/jQueryMobile/jquery.mobile-1.3.2.min.css\" />\r\n\r\n<!-- 第一页 -->\r\n<div data-role=\"page\" id=\"first\">\r\n\r\n\t<div data-role=\"header\">\r\n\t\t<h1>这是第一个页面 页头</h1>\r\n\t</div>\r\n    <!-- /header 页头 -->\r\n\r\n\t<div data-role=\"content\">\r\n        <p>这是一个 jQuery Mobile 多页切换的示例</p>\r\n        \r\n\t\t<p>\r\n            刚载入时，显示的第一个页面\r\n        </p>\r\n        \r\n\t\t<p>\r\n            点击查看 <a href=\"#second\">第二页</a>\r\n        </p>\r\n\t</div>\r\n    <!-- /content 页面内容 -->\r\n\r\n\t<div data-role=\"footer\">\r\n\t\t<h4>页脚</h4>\r\n\t</div>\r\n    <!-- /footer 页脚 -->\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!-- 第二页 -->\r\n<div data-role=\"page\" id=\"second\">\r\n\r\n\t<div data-role=\"header\">\r\n\t\t<h1>这是第二个页面 页头</h1>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\r\n\t<div data-role=\"content\">\r\n\t\t<p>这是一个 jQuery Mobile 多页切换的示例</p>\r\n        \r\n\t\t<p>\r\n            点击返回 <a href=\"#first\">第一页</a>\r\n        </p>\r\n        \r\n        <p>\r\n            也可以查看 <a href=\"#third\">第三页</a>\r\n        </p>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\r\n\t<div data-role=\"footer\">\r\n\t\t<h4>页脚</h4>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!-- 第三页 -->\r\n<div id=\"third\" data-role=\"page\">\r\n    <div data-role=\"header\">\r\n        <h1>这是第三个页面 页头</h1>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div data-role=\"content\">\r\n        <p>这是一个 jQuery Mobile 多页切换的示例</p>\r\n        \r\n        <p>\r\n            点击返回 <a href=\"#first\">第一页</a>\r\n        </p>\r\n        \r\n        <p>\r\n            点击返回 <a href=\"#second\">第二页</a>\r\n        </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div data-role=\"footer\">\r\n        <h4>页脚</h4>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"../script/lib/jQueryMobile/jquery.mobile-1.3.2.min.js\"></script>','','','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/jQueryMobile/jquery.mobile-1.3.2.min.css,../script/lib/jQueryMobile/jquery.mobile-1.3.2.min.js','jQuery Mobile-多页切换',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',1,NULL,'2013-12-11 17:17:32',NULL,NULL,'4,10,106,61,73,137','UI,jQuery,jQuery Mobile,Web,App,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (141,'<div data-role=\"page\">\r\n    <div data-role=\"header\">\r\n        <a id=\"add\" data-role=\"button\" data-icon=\"plus\" data-iconpos=\"left\" class=\"ui-btn-left\">\r\n            添加\r\n        </a>\r\n        \r\n        <h1>jQuery Mobile-手风琴效果 Accordions</h1>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div data-role=\"content\">\r\n        <div id=\"accordion\" data-role=\"collapsible-set\" data-theme=\"c\" data-content-theme=\"d\">\r\n            <div data-role=\"collapsible\">\r\n                <h3>Section 1</h3>\r\n                <p>这里是第 1 块</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div data-role=\"footer\">\r\n        <h4></h4>\r\n        <a id=\"prev\" data-role=\"button\" data-icon=\"arrow-u\" data-iconpos=\"left\" class=\"ui-btn-left\">\r\n            上一个\r\n        </a>\r\n        <a id=\"next\" data-role=\"button\" data-icon=\"arrow-d\" data-iconpos=\"left\" class=\"ui-btn-right\">\r\n            下一个\r\n        </a>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>','','$(function(){\r\n    var $accordion = $(\'#accordion\'),\r\n        num = 1,\r\n        curr = 0;\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#add\').on(\'click\', function(){\r\n        num++;\r\n        \r\n        $accordion.append(\'<div data-role=\"collapsible\">\' +\r\n                          \'<h3>Section \'+ num +\'</h3>\' +\r\n                          \'<p>这里是第 \'+ num +\' 块</p>\' +\r\n                          \'</div>\').collapsibleset(\'refresh\');\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#prev\').on(\'click\', function(){\r\n        if( curr > 0 ){\r\n            curr--;\r\n            $accordion.find(\'div[data-role=\"collapsible\"]:eq(\'+ curr +\')\').trigger(\'expand\');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#next\').on(\'click\', function(){\r\n        if( curr < num -1 ){\r\n            curr++;\r\n            $accordion.find(\'div[data-role=\"collapsible\"]:eq(\'+ curr +\')\').trigger(\'expand\');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    /**\r\n     * jQuery Moblie 构建 UI 完成时的事件\r\n     */\r\n    $(document).on(\"pageinit\", function(){\r\n        \r\n        $accordion.find(\'div[data-role=\"collapsible\"]\').trigger(\'expand\');\r\n    });\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/jQueryMobile/jquery.mobile-1.3.2.min.css,../script/lib/jQueryMobile/jquery.mobile-1.3.2.min.js','jQuery Mobile-手风琴效果 Accordions',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',1,NULL,'2013-12-12 10:44:33',NULL,NULL,'4,10,61,106,73,137','UI,jQuery,Web,jQuery Mobile,App,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (142,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>WebGL 实验-7 利用 tween.js 实现动画</h3>\r\n    <p>\r\n        tween.js 为补间动画库，作用为根据提供的关键帧，来生成关键帧之间的过渡帧\r\n    </p>\r\n    \r\n    <input type=\"button\" value=\"关闭动画\" id=\"animate\" />\r\n    <input type=\"button\" value=\"改变运动方式\" id=\"ease\" />\r\n    <div id=\"testTarget\" class=\"testTarget\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.testTarget{\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n    width: 500px;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var target = $(\'#testTarget\')[0],\r\n        renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer({\r\n            antialias: true\r\n        }),    // 渲染器\r\n        \r\n        scene = new THREE.Scene(),    // 场景\r\n        light = new THREE.PointLight(0xffffff, 2, 100),    // 光照 点光源\r\n        camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera(45, target.offsetWidth / target.offsetHeight, 1, 4000),    // 摄像机\r\n\r\n        ballGeometry = new THREE.SphereGeometry(1, 32, 32),\r\n        ballMaterial = new THREE.MeshPhongMaterial({\r\n            map: THREE.ImageUtils.loadTexture(\'../image/demo/moon_1024.jpg\')\r\n        }),\r\n        ballMesh = new THREE.Mesh(ballGeometry, ballMaterial),\r\n        \r\n        animateId = null,\r\n        run = function(){\r\n            TWEEN.update();    // 每一帧都调用了 TWEEN.update()，TWEEN.update() 会遍历当前的动画效果，并重绘它们\r\n            \r\n            renderer.render(scene, camera);\r\n            \r\n            animateId = requestAnimationFrame( run );\r\n        },\r\n        \r\n        tweensEase = true,\r\n        tweensTimeout = null,\r\n        tweens = function(){// 补间动画\r\n            var x, y, easefn;\r\n            \r\n            if( ballMesh.position.x > 0 ){\r\n                x = -3;\r\n            }\r\n            else{\r\n                x = 3;\r\n            }\r\n            \r\n            if( ballMesh.position.y > 0 ){\r\n                y = -3;\r\n                easefn = tweensEase ? TWEEN.Easing.Bounce.Out : TWEEN.Easing.Quadratic.Out;\r\n/* 原 demo 为\r\n                easefn = tweensEase ? TWEEN.Easing.Bounce.EaseOut : TWEEN.Easing.Quadratic.EaseOut;\r\n * 可能为版本原因\r\n */\r\n            }\r\n            else{\r\n                y = 3;\r\n                easefn = tweensEase ? TWEEN.Easing.Bounce.In : TWEEN.Easing.Quadratic.In;\r\n/* 原 demo 为\r\n                easefn = tweensEase ? TWEEN.Easing.Bounce.EaseIn : TWEEN.Easing.Quadratic.EaseIn;\r\n * 可能为版本原因\r\n */\r\n            }\r\n            \r\n            ( new TWEEN.Tween(ballMesh.position) ).to({\r\n                x: x,\r\n                y: y\r\n            }, 2000).easing( easefn ).start();\r\n        };\r\n    \r\n    renderer.setSize(target.offsetWidth, target.offsetHeight);\r\n    target.appendChild( renderer.domElement );\r\n    \r\n    light.position.set(0, 0, 20);\r\n    scene.add( light );\r\n    \r\n    ballMesh.position.x = -3;\r\n    ballMesh.position.y = -3;\r\n    scene.add( ballMesh );\r\n    \r\n    camera.position.set(0, 0, 15);\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#animate\').on(\'click\', function(){    // 动画开关\r\n        if( tweensTimeout ){\r\n            clearInterval( tweensTimeout );\r\n            tweensTimeout = null;\r\n            \r\n            cancelAnimationFrame( animateId );\r\n            \r\n            this.value = \'开始动画\';\r\n        }\r\n        else{\r\n            tweens();\r\n            tweensTimeout = setInterval(tweens, 2000);\r\n                        \r\n            animateId = requestAnimationFrame( run );\r\n            \r\n            this.value = \'关闭动画\';\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n    $(\'#ease\').on(\'click\', function(){\r\n        tweensEase = !tweensEase;\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    tweens();\r\n    tweensTimeout = setInterval(tweens, 2000);\r\n    \r\n    run();\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/three/three.min.js,../script/lib/tween/tween.min.js','WebGL 实验-7 利用 tween.js 实现动画',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',3,NULL,'2013-12-13 16:29:13',NULL,NULL,'99,92,105,3,137','three.js,WebGL,动画效果,HTML5,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (143,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>JavaScript 设计模式-单例模式</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <div id=\"testResult\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}','/**\r\n * 基类\r\n * @class  Robot\r\n */\r\nfunction Robot(){}\r\nRobot.prototype.hi = function(){\r\n    return this.hello;\r\n};\r\n/**\r\n * 继承类\r\n * @class  RobotMaker\r\n */\r\nfunction RobotMaker(name){  // 构造函数\r\n    if( !(this instanceof RobotMaker) ){\r\n        return new RobotMaker(name);\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    var onlyOne, makeNum = 0,\r\n        Robots = [],\r\n        index = 0;\r\n    \r\n    if( typeof RobotMaker.onlyOne === \'object\' ){\r\n        return RobotMaker.onlyOne;\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    this.name = name;\r\n    this.type = \'RobotMaker\';\r\n    this.makeNum = 0;\r\n    this.hello = \'Hi, I\\\'m a Robot, and I\\\'m the only one RobotMaker, you don\\\'t need the second, my name is \'+ this.name;\r\n    \r\n    RobotMaker.onlyOne = this;\r\n    \r\n    return this;\r\n}\r\nRobotMaker.prototype = new Robot();\r\n\r\n$(function(){\r\n    // test\r\n    var r1 = new RobotMaker(\'r1\'),\r\n        r2 = new RobotMaker(\'r2\'),\r\n        \r\n        $testResult = $(\'#testResult\');\r\n    \r\n    $testResult.append(\'<p>\'+ r1.hi() +\'</p>\');\r\n    $testResult.append(\'<p>\'+ r2.hi() +\'</p>\');\r\n    \r\n    console && console.log( r1.hi() );\r\n    console && console.log( r2.hi() );\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js','JavaScript 设计模式-单例模式',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',1,NULL,'2013-12-14 09:53:38',NULL,NULL,'6,56,48,137','JavaScript,设计模式,原创,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (144,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>WebGL 实验-8 导入模型</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"testTarget\" id=\"testTarget\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.testTarget{\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n    width: 500px;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var target = $(\'#testTarget\')[0],\r\n        renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer({\r\n            antialias: true\r\n        }),    // 渲染器\r\n        \r\n        scene = new THREE.Scene(),    // 场景\r\n        light = new THREE.DirectionalLight(0x777777, 1),    // 光照\r\n        camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera(45, target.offsetWidth / target.offsetHeight, 1, 4000),    // 摄像机\r\n\r\n        robotBody = new THREE.Object3D(),\r\n        \r\n        loader = new THREE.ColladaLoader(),\r\n        animate = function(param){\r\n            var duration = param.duration || 1000,\r\n                loop = param.loop || false,\r\n                i, l, temp, interp;\r\n            \r\n            for(i = 0, l = param.interps.length; i < l; i++){\r\n                temp = param.interps[i];\r\n                interp = a;\r\n            }\r\n        },\r\n        run = function(){\r\n            renderer.render(scene, camera);\r\n            \r\n            robotBody.rotation.y += 0.01;\r\n            \r\n            requestAnimationFrame( run );\r\n        };\r\n    \r\n    renderer.setSize(target.offsetWidth, target.offsetHeight);\r\n    target.appendChild( renderer.domElement );\r\n    \r\n    light.position.set(0, 0, 1);\r\n    scene.add( light );\r\n    \r\n    loader.load(\'../image/demo/robot/robot_cartoon_02.dae\', function(data){\r\n        var model, that;\r\n        \r\n        if( data ){\r\n            model = data.scene;\r\n            model.scale.set(0.01, 0.01, 0.01);    // 原模型使用的单位是里面，而程序中的单位是米，所以进行转换\r\n            \r\n            robotBody.add( model );\r\n            console.dir(robotBody)\r\n            /*\r\n             * 原 demo 使用 THREE.SceneUtils.traverseHierarchy 方法，因为版本原因\r\n             */\r\n            robotBody.traverse(function(n){\r\n                switch( n.name ){\r\n                    case \'jambe_G\':\r\n                        robotBody.left_leg = n;\r\n                        break;\r\n                    case \'jambe_D\':\r\n                        robotBody.right_leg = n;\r\n                        break;\r\n                    case \'head_container\':\r\n                        robotBody.head = n;\r\n                        break;\r\n                    case \'clef\':\r\n                        robotBody.key = n;\r\n                        break;\r\n                    default:\r\n                        break;\r\n                }\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    scene.add( robotBody );\r\n    \r\n    camera.position.set(0, 2.333, 8);\r\n    \r\n    var keys = [0, 0.25, 0.5, 0.75, 1];\r\n    animate({\r\n        interps: [{    // body\r\n            keys: keys,\r\n            values: [{\r\n                x: 0\r\n            }, {\r\n                x: -Math.PI /48\r\n            }, {\r\n                x: 0\r\n            }, {\r\n                x: Math.PI /48\r\n            }, {\r\n                x: 0\r\n            }],\r\n            target: robotBody.rotation\r\n        }, {    // head\r\n            keys: keys,\r\n            values: [{\r\n                z: 0\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: -Math.PI /96\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: 0\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: Math.PI /96\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: 0\r\n            }],\r\n            target: robotBody.head.rotation\r\n        }, {    // key\r\n            keys: keys,\r\n            values: [{\r\n                x: 0\r\n            }, {\r\n                x: Math.PI /4\r\n            }, {\r\n                x: Math.PI /2\r\n            }, {\r\n                x: Math.PI *3/4\r\n            }, {\r\n                x: Math.PI\r\n            }],\r\n            target: robotBody.key.rotation\r\n        }, {    // leftLeg\r\n            keys: keys,\r\n            values: [{\r\n                z: 0\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: Math.PI /6\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: 0\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: 0\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: 0\r\n            }],\r\n            target: robotBody.left_leg.rotation\r\n        }, {    // rightLeg\r\n            keys: keys,\r\n            values: [{\r\n                z: 0\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: 0\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: 0\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: Math.PI /6\r\n            }, {\r\n                z: 0\r\n            }],\r\n            target: robotBody.right_leg.rotation\r\n        }]\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    //run();\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/three/three.min.js,../script/lib/three/ColladaLoader.js','WebGL 实验-8 导入模型',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',3,NULL,'2013-12-16 16:37:47',NULL,NULL,'3,99,92,137','HTML5,three.js,WebGL,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (145,'<div class=\"container\">\r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            <h1>h1. 一级标题 <small>一级标题字体 36px <code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> 标签或 .h1 类</small></h1>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            <h2>h2. 二级标题 <small>二级标题字体 30px <code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> 标签或 .h2 类</small></h2>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            <h3>h3. 三级标题 <small>三级标题字体 24px <code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> 标签或 .h3 类</small></h3>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            <h4>h4. 四级标题 <small>四级标题字体 18px <code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> 标签或 .h4 类</small></h4>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            <h5>h5. 五级标题 <small>五级标题字体 14px <code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> 标签或 .h5 类</small></h5>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            <h6>h6. 六级标题 <small>六级标题字体 12px <code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> 标签或 .h6 类</small></h6>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            <h1>主标题</h1>\r\n            \r\n            <p><code>&lt;p&gt;</code> 用来显示主要文字，可以加入内联标签 <small><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> 标签或 .small 类来显示小号文本</small>，\r\n                加入 <strong><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code> 标签来显示强调文本</strong>，\r\n                加入 <em><code>&lt;em&gt;</code> 标签来显示斜体，也可以用 <code>&lt;i&gt;</code>、<code>&lt;b&gt;</code> 标签</em>\r\n            </p>\r\n            \r\n            <p class=\"lead\">对 <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> 标签的 class 添加 lead，变成一段重点突出的文字</p>\r\n            \r\n            <p class=\"text-left\">对 <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> 标签的 class 添加 text-left 将文字变成左对齐</p>\r\n            \r\n            <p class=\"text-center\">对 <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> 标签的 class 添加 text-center 将文字变成居中</p>\r\n            \r\n            <p class=\"text-right\">对 <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> 标签的 class 添加 text-right 将文字变成右对齐</p>\r\n            \r\n            <p class=\"text-primary\">对 <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> 标签的 class 添加 text-muted、text-primary、text-success、\r\n                text-info、text-warning、text-danger 将文字变成不同类型的强调</p>\r\n            \r\n            <p>用 <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> 标签来表示缩略语，如 <abbr title=\"attribute\">attr</abbr>；用 <code>&lt;address&gt;</code> 标签来\r\n                表示地址</p>\r\n            \r\n            <blockquote class=\"pull-right\">\r\n                <p>用 <code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code> 标签来表示引用，对 class 添加 pull-right 来展现出向右侧移动、对齐的效果，\r\n                    添加 <code>&lt;small&gt;</code> 标签或 .small 类来注明引用来源，来源名称可以放在 <code>&lt;cite&gt;</code> 标签里面</p>\r\n                \r\n                <small>http://v3.bootcss.com/css/#type</small>\r\n            </blockquote>\r\n            \r\n            <p>在正文中通过 <code>&lt;code&gt;</code> 标签包裹内联样式的代码片段，\r\n                多行代码可以使用 <code>&lt;pre&gt;</code> 标签。为了正确的展示代码，注意将尖括号做转义处理。</p>\r\n            \r\n            <pre>&lt;p&gt;Sample text here...&lt;/p&gt;</pre>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>','.row{\r\n    margin: 15px 0;\r\n}\r\n.row div{\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n    border: 1px solid #DDD;\r\n    border-radius: 10px;\r\n    \r\n    background-color: #efefef;\r\n}\r\np{\r\n    background: #efefef;\r\n}','','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/js/bootstrap.min.js','Bootstrap 框架实践-2 排版',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',4,NULL,'2013-12-17 13:10:13',NULL,NULL,'98,4,137','Bootstrap,UI,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (146,'<div class=\"container\">\r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            <h1>列表</h1>\r\n            \r\n            <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\r\n                <li>这是一个无序列表</li>\r\n                <li>对列表添加 list-unstyled 类可以去除列表样式，但不会影响到子列表</li>\r\n                <li>列表可以嵌套\r\n                    <ul>\r\n                        <li>这是一个子列表</li>\r\n                        <li>列表项 2</li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>也可嵌套有序列表\r\n                    <ol>\r\n                        <li>这是一个有序列表</li>\r\n                        <li>列表项 2</li>\r\n                    </ol>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>对列表添加 list-inline 类可以变成内联列表\r\n                    <ul class=\"list-inline\">\r\n                        <li>这是一个内联列表</li>\r\n                        <li>列表项 2</li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>描述列表\r\n                    <dl>\r\n                        <dt>描述列表</dt>\r\n                        <dd>带有描述的短语列表</dd>\r\n                        <dt>描述短语 2</dt>\r\n                        <dd>描述 2</dd>\r\n                    </dl>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>对描述列表添加 dl-horizontal 类，可以让短语与描述排在一行\r\n                    <dl class=\"dl-horizontal\">\r\n                        <dt>横向描述列表</dt>\r\n                        <dd>描述 1</dd>\r\n                        <dt>短语 2</dt>\r\n                        <dd>描述 2</dd>\r\n                    </dl>\r\n                </li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>','.row{\r\n    margin: 15px 0;\r\n}\r\n.row div{\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n    border: 1px solid #DDD;\r\n    border-radius: 10px;\r\n    \r\n    background-color: #efefef;\r\n}','','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/js/bootstrap.min.js','Bootstrap 框架实践-3 列表',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',4,NULL,'2013-12-17 14:55:01',NULL,NULL,'4,98,137','UI,Bootstrap,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (147,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>jQuery UI-弹窗 Dialog</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <input type=\"button\" value=\"弹出\" id=\"popup\" class=\"btn\" />\r\n    <div id=\"dialog\" class=\"test hidden\" title=\"jQuery UI 弹窗测试\">\r\n        <p>这是一个默认的 jQuery UI 弹窗</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.hidden{\r\n    display: none;\r\n}','$(function() {\r\n    var $dialog = $(\'#dialog\').dialog({\r\n        autoOpen: false,    // 默认关闭\r\n        closeOnEscape: false,    // ESC 不控制关闭\r\n        height: 400,    // 设定弹窗高度\r\n        maxHeight: 600,    // 最大高度\r\n        minHeight: 200,    // 最小高度\r\n        width: 400,    // 设定弹窗宽度\r\n        maxWidth: 600,    // 最大宽度\r\n        minWidth: 200,    // 最小宽度\r\n        resizable: false,    // 禁止缩放，默认为 true\r\n        modal: true,    // lightbox 背景\r\n        draggable: false,    // 禁止拖拽，默认为 true\r\n        position:{\r\n            at: \'center top\'\r\n        },\r\n        show:{    // 显示效果\r\n            effect: \'explode\',\r\n            duration: 800\r\n        },\r\n        hide:{    // 消失效果\r\n            effect: \'blind\',\r\n            duration: 1000\r\n        },\r\n        buttons:[{\r\n            text: \'确定\',\r\n            click: function(){\r\n                // 关闭弹窗\r\n                $dialog.dialog(\'close\');\r\n            }\r\n        }, {\r\n            text: \'改变内容\',\r\n            click: function(){\r\n                $dialog.html(\'这是改变后的内容\');\r\n            }\r\n        }]\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#popup\').on(\'click\', function(){\r\n        $dialog.dialog(\'open\')\r\n    });\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.css,../script/lib/jQueryUI/jquery-ui-1.10.3.custom.min.js','jQuery UI-弹窗 Dialog',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',1,NULL,'2013-12-17 18:36:56',NULL,NULL,'10,4,96,137','jQuery,UI,jQuery UI,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (148,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>D3 数据可视化-8</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"testTarget\" id=\"testTarget\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\ncircle {\r\n  fill: rgb(31, 119, 180);\r\n  fill-opacity: .25;\r\n  stroke: rgb(31, 119, 180);\r\n  stroke-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.leaf circle {\r\n  fill: #ff7f0e;\r\n  fill-opacity: 1;\r\n}\r\n\r\ntext {\r\n  font: 12px sans-serif;\r\n}','var data = {\r\n    name: \'前端工程师\',\r\n    children: [{\r\n        name: \'切页面\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'HTML\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'CSS\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'PhotoShop\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'编程语言\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'Javascript\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'PHP/Python/Perl/Ruby/BashShell...\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'NodeJS/FlashAS\', group: 2\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'测试工具\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'Firebug/Firebug-lite/Web Inspector\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'YSlow/Smushit\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'IEDeveloper/IETester\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'SuperPreview/JsBeautifier\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'Fiddler/WireShark/tcpdump\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'开发工具\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'VIM/Aptana/Notepad++/EditPlus...\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'SygWin/svn/git\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'计算机知识储备\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'编译原理/计算机网络\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'操作系统/算法原理\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'软件工程/软件测试原理\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'前端标准/规范\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'w3c/DOM/BOM/XHTML/XML/JSON/JSONP\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'HTML5/CSS3\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'ECMAScript3/ECMAScript5\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'CommonJS/AMD\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'HTTP1.1\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'性能\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'WebPageTest\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'ShowSlow/YSlow/34Rule\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'PageSpeed\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'HttpWatch\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'DynaTrace\\\'s Ajax\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'编程知识储备\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'数据结构/MVC\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'面向对象/切面编程\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'函数式编程\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'JavaScript设计模式\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'JavaScript编程模式\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'Web服务\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'YQL/Company Open Platform\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'APP Engine/Cloud\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'Google Open API/Github\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'前沿技术社区/会议\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'YDN/YUIConf/JSConf\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'QCon/Velocity\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'D2/WebRebuild\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'NodeParty/HTML5研究小组\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'UED Teams\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'移动终端\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'jQueryMobile/HTML5/CSS3\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'iPhone/iPad/iOS/Android\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'Responsive UI Design\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'安全\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'CSRF/XSS\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'ADsafe/Caja/FBJS/SandBox\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'软技能\',\r\n        children: [{\r\n            name: \'知识管理/总结分享\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'沟通技巧/团队开发/需求管理/PM\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'代码模块化开发/代码版本管理\'\r\n        }, {\r\n            name: \'交互设计/可用性/可访问性知识\'\r\n        }]\r\n    }],\r\n};\r\n$(function(){\r\n    var diameter = 850,\r\n        format = d3.format(\',d\'),\r\n\r\n        // d3.layou.pack() d3 布局方法 基于递归圆形填充\r\n        pack = d3.layout.pack().size([diameter - 4, diameter - 4]).value(function(d){\r\n            return d.size || 5000;\r\n        }),\r\n\r\n        svg = d3.select(\'#testTarget\').append(\'svg\').attr(\'width\', diameter).attr(\'height\', diameter)\r\n                .append(\'g\').attr(\'transform\', \'translate(2,2)\'),\r\n\r\n        node = svg.datum( data ).selectAll(\'.node\').data( pack.nodes ).enter().append(\'g\').attr(\'class\', function(d){\r\n                    return d.children ? \'node\' : \'leaf node\';\r\n                }).attr(\'transform\', function(d){\r\n                    return \'translate(\' + d.x + \',\' + d.y + \')\';\r\n                });\r\n\r\n    node.append(\'title\').text(function(d){\r\n        return d.name;    // + (d.children ? \'\' : \': \' + format(d.size || 5000));\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    node.append(\'circle\').attr(\'r\', function(d){\r\n        return d.r;\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    node.filter(function(d){\r\n        return !d.children;\r\n    }).append(\'text\').style(\'text-anchor\', \'middle\').text(function(d) {\r\n        return d.name.substring(0, d.r /3);\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    //d3.select(self.frameElement).style(\'height\', diameter + \'px\');\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/d3/d3.v3.min.js','D3 数据可视化-8',NULL,'../image/preview/d3-7.jpg',4,NULL,'2013-12-18 10:52:39',NULL,NULL,'97,55,104','D3.js,数据可视化,SVG');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (149,'<!--\r\n    模板\r\n    <script type=\"text/x-handlebars\"> 代表我们的应用模板。\r\n    应用模板使用 {{outlet}} 标签为其他模板预留位置，其内容取决于url\r\n\r\n    用 {#link-to}} 创建了一个指向路由的链接\r\n-->\r\n<script type=\"text/x-handlebars\">\r\n<nav class=\"navbar navbar-default navbar-inverse\" role=\"navigation\">\r\n    <div class=\"navbar-header\">\r\n        <a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"#\">首页</a>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right text-right\">\r\n        <li>{{#link-to \'feedback\'}}<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></span> 反馈问题{{/link-to}}</li>\r\n        <li>{{#link-to \'list\'}}<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-plus\"></span> 反馈列表{{/link-to}}</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</nav>\r\n                 \r\n<div id=\"main\" class=\"container case\">\r\n    {{outlet}}\r\n</div>\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- 首页 -->\r\n<script type=\"text/x-handlebars\" id=\"index\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n        <h3>Ember 框架实践</h3>\r\n        \r\n        <p>\r\n            Ember 是一个客户端的 JavaScript MV* 框架，用来构建 web 应用，它依赖于 jQuery 和 Handlebars 库，Ember 可以为你完成很多事情，\r\n            如果你遵循它的命名约定的话。以下为 Ember 的四个核心概念：</p>\r\n        \r\n        <ol>\r\n            <li>模型</li>\r\n            <li>路由</li>\r\n            <li>控制器</li>\r\n            <li>模板</li>\r\n        </ol>\r\n        \r\n        <p>\r\n            参考教程：\r\n            <a href=\"http://segmentfault.com/a/1190000000365519\">\r\n                http://segmentfault.com/a/1190000000365519\r\n            </a>\r\n        </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- 反馈问题表单 -->\r\n<script type=\"text/x-handlebars\" id=\"feedback\">\r\n<form class=\"form-horizontal\" role=\"form\" action=\"#rs/result\">\r\n    <h3>反馈问题</h3>\r\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n        <label for=\"title\" class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">标题</label>\r\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\r\n            <input type=\"title\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"title\" name=\"title\" placeholder=\"请输入标题\" required>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n        <label for=\"excerpt\" class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">详细描述</label>\r\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\r\n            <textarea class=\"form-control\" id=\"excerpt\" name=\"excerpt\" placeholder=\"请详细的描述所遇到的问题\" required></textarea>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n        <label for=\"email\" class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Email</label>\r\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\r\n            <input type=\"url\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"请输入您的 Email\" required>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n        <label for=\"fullname\" class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">您的昵称</label>\r\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\r\n            <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"请输入您的昵称\" required>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\r\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-success\" {{action \'save\'}}>提交</button>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</form>\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- 反馈问题列表 -->\r\n<script type=\"text/x-handlebars\" id=\"list\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n        <table class=\'table\'>\r\n            <thead>\r\n                <tr><th>反馈列表</th></tr>\r\n            </thead>\r\n            <tbody>\r\n            {{#each controller}}\r\n                <tr><td>{{#link-to \'detail\' this}}{{title}}{{/link-to}}</td></tr>\r\n            {{/each}}\r\n            </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n        {{outlet}}\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- 反馈问题详细 -->\r\n<script type=\"text/x-handlebars\" id=\"detail\">\r\n<h1>{{title}}</h1>\r\n<h2> by {{name}} <small class=\"muted\">{{submittedOn}}</small></h2>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">\r\n    {{excerpt}}\r\n</p>\r\n</script>','.case{\r\n    border-radius: 10px;\r\n    margin: 60px auto 0; \r\n    background-color: #efefef;\r\n}','/**\r\n * \r\n */\r\n$(function(){\r\n    // 创建 Ember 应用实例\r\n    var App = Ember.Application.create();\r\n\r\n    /**\r\n     * 定义应用的路径\r\n     * 每个 Ember 应用都有一个默认路由 Index，绑定到 /\r\n     */\r\n    App.Router.map(function(){\r\n        this.resource(\'feedback\', {\r\n            path: \'fb/new\'\r\n        });\r\n        this.resource(\'list\', {\r\n            path: \'fb/list\'\r\n        }, function(){\r\n            // 嵌套路由\r\n            this.resource(\'detail\', {\r\n                //:fb_id 部分叫做动态字段，因为相应的报道 id 会被注入URL\r\n                path: \'/detail/:fb_id\'\r\n            });\r\n        });\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    // 本地存储适配器\r\n    App.ApplicationAdapter = DS.LSAdapter.extend({\r\n        namespace: \'stories\'\r\n    });\r\n    App.Feedback = DS.Model.extend({\r\n        email: DS.attr(\'string\'),\r\n        name: DS.attr(\'string\'),\r\n        title: DS.attr(\'string\'),\r\n        excerpt: DS.attr(\'string\'),\r\n        submittedOn: DS.attr(\'date\')    \r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    // 控制器\r\n    App.FeedbackController = Ember.ObjectController.extend({\r\n        actions: {\r\n            save: function(){\r\n                var store = this.get(\'store\'),    // 调用本地存储\r\n                    fb = store.createRecord(\'feedback\', {\r\n                        email: $(\'#email\').val(),\r\n                        name: $(\'#name\').val(),\r\n                        title: $(\'#title\').val(),\r\n                        excerpt: $(\'#excerpt\').val(),\r\n                        submittedOn: new Date()\r\n                    });\r\n                \r\n                fb.save();\r\n                this.transitionToRoute(\'list\');    // url 跳转\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n    App.ListController = Ember.ArrayController.extend({\r\n        sortProperties: [\'submittedOn\'],\r\n        sortAscending: false\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    // 模型\r\n    App.ListRoute = Ember.Route.extend({\r\n        model : function(){\r\n            return this.get(\'store\').findAll(\'feedback\');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n    App.DetailRoute = Ember.Route.extend({\r\n        model: function( params ){\r\n            return this.get(\'store\').find(\'feedback\', params.story_id);\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/js/bootstrap.min.js,../script/lib/handlebars/handlebars-v1.1.2.js,../script/lib/ember/ember-1.2.0.min.js,../script/lib/ember/ember-data.js,../script/lib/ember/localstorage_adapter.js','Ember 框架实践',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',1,NULL,'2013-12-21 10:49:14',NULL,NULL,'6,11,119,132,137','JavaScript,框架,Ember.js,MV*,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (150,'<div class=\"container case\" ng-app>\r\n<!--     ng-init 指令 初始化数据\r\n    <div class=\"row\" ng-init=\"books=[{\'name\': \'Effective Java\', \'author\':\'Joshua Bloch\'},{\'name\': \'Year without Pants\', \'author\':\'Scott Berkun\'},{ \'name\':\'Confessions of public speaker\',\'author\':\'Scott Berkun\'},{\'name\':\'JavaScript Good Parts\',\'author\':\'Douglas Crockford\'}]\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            <h2>Your Online Bookshop</h2>\r\n            <input type=\"search\" ng-model=\"criteria\">\r\n        \r\n            <ul class=\"unstyled\">\r\n                ng-repeat 指令 遍历集合中的所有元素\r\n        \r\n                     filter 搜索过滤器\r\n                     orderBy 排序过滤器\r\n                <li ng-repeat=\"book in books | filter: criteria | orderBy: \'name\'\">\r\n                    uppercase 过滤器 大写\r\n                    <span>{{book.name}} written by {{book.author | uppercase}}</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n     -->      \r\n    \r\n    <!-- ng-controller 指令 调用控制器 -->\r\n    <div class=\"row\" ng-controller=\"BookCtrl\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            <h1>Angular 框架实践-1</h1>\r\n            <p>参考教程：\r\n                <a href=\"http://segmentfault.com/a/1190000000350125\">\r\n                    http://segmentfault.com/a/1190000000350125\r\n                </a>\r\n            </p>\r\n\r\n            <h2>读书列表</h2>\r\n            <div class=\"from-group\">\r\n                <input type=\"search\" class=\"form-control\" ng-model=\"search\" placeholder=\"搜索您要找的书\" />\r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n            <ul>\r\n                <li ng-repeat=\"book in books | filter: search | orderBy: \'name\'\">\r\n                    <h4>{{book.name}}</h4>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-right\">作者：{{book.author}}</p>\r\n                </li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border-radius: 10px;\r\n    margin: 10px auto 0; \r\n    background-color: #efefef;\r\n    font-family: \"Consolas\",Monaco,Andale,monospace;\r\n}','var data = [{\r\n        name: \'JavaScript 模式\',\r\n        author: \'Stoyan Stefanov\'\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'基于 MVC 的 JavaScript Web 富应用开发\',\r\n        author: \'Alex MacCaw\'\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'编写可维护的 JavaScript\',\r\n        author: \'Nicbolas C.Zakas\'\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'JavaScript 语言精粹（修订版）\',\r\n        author: \'Douglas Crockford\'\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'CSS 禅意花园（修订版）\',\r\n        author: \'Dave Shea,Molly E.Holzschlag\'\r\n    },{\r\n        name: \'WebGL 入门指南\',\r\n        author: \'Tony Parisi\'\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'数据可视化实战：使用D3设计交互式图表\',\r\n        author: \'Scott Murray\'\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'实时用户体验\',\r\n        author: \'Ted Roden\'\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'Node 即学即用\',\r\n        author: \'Tom Hugbes-Croicber,Mike Wilson\'\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'微交互：细节设计成就卓越产品\',\r\n        author: \'Dan Saffer\'\r\n    }, {\r\n        name: \'精益创业：新创业的成长思维\',\r\n        author: \'Eric Ries\'\r\n    }\r\n];\r\nfunction BookCtrl($scope){\r\n    $scope.books = data;\r\n}\r\nwindow.BookCtrl = BookCtrl;\r\n\r\n$(function(){\r\n    /**\r\n     * 页面中需要定义 ng-app，这将初始化 AngularJS 应用程序，\r\n     * 并告诉 AngularJS 要在这一部分活跃\r\n     * 大多数情况下应用程序里是活跃整个 html 文件的，\r\n     * 所以 ng-app 标签通常写在 html标签上\r\n     */\r\n    //$(\'html\').attr(\'ng-app\', \'\');\r\n    \r\n    /**\r\n     * 初始化 angular\r\n     * 由于这里的结构问题，只能使用这种方法加载并初始化 angular，\r\n     * 在实际项目中，则可以将将其写在 html 页面代码中\r\n     */\r\n    $(\'<script src=\"..\\/script\\/lib/angular\\/angular.min.js\"><\\/script>\').appendTo(\'body\');\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/js/bootstrap.min.js','Angular 框架实践-1',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',1,NULL,'2013-12-23 11:25:16',NULL,NULL,'6,11,121,132,137','JavaScript,框架,Angular.js,MV*,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (151,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>D3 数据可视化-9</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <input type=\"button\" value=\"定格排序\" id=\"sort\" />\r\n    <div class=\"testTarget\" id=\"testTarget\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\ntext{\r\n    text-anchor: middle;\r\n    font-family: sans-serif;\r\n    font-size: 11px;\r\n    fill: white;\r\n}','$(function(){       \r\n    var w = 600,\r\n        h = 250,\r\n        \r\n        dataset = [ 5, 10, 13, 19, 21, 25, 22, 18, 15, 13, 11, 12, 15, 20, 18, 17, 16, 18, 23, 25 ],\r\n        \r\n        color = d3.scale.category20(),\r\n        \r\n        xScale = d3.scale.ordinal().domain(d3.range(dataset.length))    // d3.range(n) 生成长度为 n 的连续数值数组\r\n                    .rangeRoundBands([0, w], 0.05),\r\n        // rangeRoundBands() 自动分档并自动舍入到最近的整数值 并设置 5% 的间距\r\n        \r\n        yScale = d3.scale.linear().domain([0, d3.max(dataset)]).range([0, h]).clamp(true),\r\n        // 强制所有输出值都位于指定范围内，超出范围的值，会被取整到范围的最高或最低值，当前为 25 和 0\r\n        \r\n        svg = d3.select(\'#testTarget\').append(\'svg\').attr(\'width\', w).attr(\'height\', h),    // 创建 SVG\r\n        \r\n        maxValue = 30;    // 设置测试数据最高值\r\n    \r\n    // 创建柱形图\r\n    svg.selectAll(\'rect\').data(dataset).enter().append(\'rect\').attr(\'x\', function(d, i){\r\n        return xScale(i);\r\n    }).attr(\'y\', function(d){\r\n        return h - yScale(d);\r\n    }).attr(\'width\', xScale.rangeBand())    // 使用 自动分档\r\n        .attr(\'height\', function(d){\r\n            return yScale(d);\r\n        }).attr(\'fill\', function(d, i){\r\n            return color( i );\r\n        });\r\n    \r\n    // 创建数据标签\r\n    svg.selectAll(\'text\').data(dataset).enter().append(\'text\').text(function(d){\r\n        return d;\r\n    }).attr(\'x\', function(d, i){\r\n        return xScale(i) + xScale.rangeBand() /2;\r\n    }).attr(\'y\', function(d){\r\n        return h - yScale(d) +14;\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    var transition = true,\r\n        interval = null,\r\n        run = function(){\r\n            interval = setInterval(function(){\r\n                // 生成随机数据\r\n                var numValues = dataset.length,\r\n                    i = 0;\r\n                                \r\n                // 更新比例尺\r\n                // yScale.domain([0, d3.max(dataset)]);\r\n                \r\n                // 更新柱形图\r\n                svg.selectAll(\'rect\').data(dataset).transition().delay(function(d, i){\r\n                    return i / dataset.length *1000;\r\n                }).duration(500).attr(\'y\', function(d){\r\n                    return h - yScale(d);\r\n                }).attr(\'height\', function(d){\r\n                    return yScale(d);\r\n//                }).attr(\'fill\', function(d, i){\r\n//                    return color( i+1 );\r\n                });\r\n                \r\n                // 更新图表数据\r\n                svg.selectAll(\'text\').data(dataset).transition().delay(function (d, i){\r\n                    return i / dataset.length *1000;\r\n                }).duration(500).text(function(d){\r\n                    return d;\r\n                }).attr(\'x\', function(d, i){\r\n                    return xScale(i) + xScale.rangeBand() /2;\r\n                }).attr(\'y\', function(d){\r\n                    return h - yScale(d) +14;\r\n                });\r\n                \r\n                dataset = [];\r\n                for(; i < numValues; i++){\r\n                    dataset.push( Math.floor( Math.random() * maxValue ) );\r\n                }\r\n            }, 1000);\r\n        };\r\n    \r\n    d3.select(\'#sort\').on(\'click\', function(){    // 绑定点击事件\r\n        if( transition ){\r\n            clearInterval( interval );\r\n            transition = false;\r\n            interval = null;\r\n            \r\n            this.value = \'继续变化\';\r\n            \r\n            svg.selectAll(\'rect\').sort(function(a, b){\r\n                return d3.ascending(a, b);\r\n            }).transition().delay(2000).duration(1000).attr(\'x\', function(d, i){\r\n                return xScale(i);\r\n            });\r\n            svg.selectAll(\'text\').sort(function(a, b){\r\n                return d3.ascending(a, b);\r\n            }).transition().delay(2000).duration(1000).attr(\'x\', function(d, i){\r\n                return xScale(i) + xScale.rangeBand() /2;\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        else{\r\n            this.value = \'定格排序\';\r\n            transition = true;\r\n            run();\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    run();\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/d3/d3.v3.min.js','D3 数据可视化-9',NULL,'../image/preview/d3-9.jpg',NULL,NULL,'2013-12-27 17:11:24',NULL,NULL,'104,97,55','SVG,D3.js,数据可视化');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (152,'<div class=\"container\">\r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            \r\n            <h4>基本表格样式 <code>&lt;table class=\"table\"&gt;</code></h4>\r\n            \r\n            <table class=\"table\">\r\n                <thead>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <th>Id</th>\r\n                        <th>姓</th>\r\n                        <th>名</th>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </thead>\r\n                \r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>1</td>\r\n                        <td>张</td>\r\n                        <td>三</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>2</td>\r\n                        <td>李</td>\r\n                        <td>四</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>3</td>\r\n                        <td>王</td>\r\n                        <td>二</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            \r\n            <h4>条纹状表格 <code>&lt;table class=\"table table-striped\"&gt;</code></h4>\r\n            \r\n            <table class=\"table table-striped\">\r\n                <thead>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <th>Id</th>\r\n                        <th>姓</th>\r\n                        <th>名</th>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </thead>\r\n                \r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>1</td>\r\n                        <td>张</td>\r\n                        <td>三</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>2</td>\r\n                        <td>李</td>\r\n                        <td>四</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>3</td>\r\n                        <td>王</td>\r\n                        <td>二</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            \r\n            <h4>带边框的表格 <code>&lt;table class=\"table table-bordered\"&gt;</code></h4>\r\n            \r\n            <table class=\"table table-bordered\">\r\n                <thead>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <th>Id</th>\r\n                        <th>姓</th>\r\n                        <th>名</th>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </thead>\r\n                \r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>1</td>\r\n                        <td>张</td>\r\n                        <td>三</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>2</td>\r\n                        <td>李</td>\r\n                        <td>四</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>3</td>\r\n                        <td>王</td>\r\n                        <td>二</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            \r\n            <h4>带鼠标悬停效果的表格 <code>&lt;table class=\"table table-hover\"&gt;</code></h4>\r\n            \r\n            <table class=\"table table-hover\">\r\n                <thead>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <th>Id</th>\r\n                        <th>姓</th>\r\n                        <th>名</th>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </thead>\r\n                \r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>1</td>\r\n                        <td>张</td>\r\n                        <td>三</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>2</td>\r\n                        <td>李</td>\r\n                        <td>四</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>3</td>\r\n                        <td>王</td>\r\n                        <td>二</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            \r\n            <h4>紧缩表格 <code>&lt;table class=\"table table-condensed\"&gt;</code></h4>\r\n            \r\n            <table class=\"table table-condensed\">\r\n                <thead>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <th>Id</th>\r\n                        <th>姓</th>\r\n                        <th>名</th>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </thead>\r\n                \r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>1</td>\r\n                        <td>张</td>\r\n                        <td>三</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>2</td>\r\n                        <td>李</td>\r\n                        <td>四</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>3</td>\r\n                        <td>王</td>\r\n                        <td>二</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            \r\n            <h4>对行、单元格添加状态</h4>\r\n            \r\n            <table class=\"table\">\r\n                <thead>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <th>Id</th>\r\n                        <th>姓</th>\r\n                        <th>名</th>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </thead>\r\n                \r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr class=\"active\">\r\n                        <td>1</td>\r\n                        <td>张</td>\r\n                        <td>三</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr class=\"danger\">\r\n                        <td>2</td>\r\n                        <td>李</td>\r\n                        <td>四</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td>3</td>\r\n                        <td>王</td>\r\n                        <td class=\"warning\">二</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>','.row{\r\n    margin: 15px 0;\r\n}\r\n.row div{\r\n    border: 1px solid #DDD;\r\n    border-radius: 10px;\r\n    \r\n    background-color: #efefef;\r\n    \r\n    line-height: 40px;\r\n}','','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/js/bootstrap.min.js','Bootstrap 框架实践-4 表格',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',NULL,NULL,'2014-01-03 10:40:18',NULL,NULL,'4,98,137','UI,Bootstrap,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (153,'<div class=\"container\">\r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            \r\n            <h3>表单</h3>\r\n            \r\n            <form role=\"form\">\r\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                    <label for=\"exampleInputEmail1\">电子邮箱</label>\r\n                    <input type=\"email\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"exampleInputEmail1\" placeholder=\"电子邮箱\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                    <label for=\"exampleInputPassword1\">密码</label>\r\n                    <input type=\"password\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"exampleInputPassword1\" placeholder=\"密码\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                    <label for=\"exampleInputFile\">File input</label>\r\n                    <input type=\"file\" id=\"exampleInputFile\">\r\n                    <p class=\"help-block\">Example block-level help text here.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"checkbox\">\r\n                    <label>\r\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\"> Check me out\r\n                    </label>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-default\">Submit</button>\r\n            </form>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            \r\n            <h3>内联表单</h3>\r\n            \r\n            <form class=\"form-inline\" role=\"form\">\r\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                    <label class=\"sr-only\" for=\"exampleInputEmail2\">电子邮箱</label>\r\n                    <input type=\"email\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"exampleInputEmail2\" placeholder=\"电子邮箱\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                    <label class=\"sr-only\" for=\"exampleInputPassword2\">密码</label>\r\n                    <input type=\"password\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"exampleInputPassword2\" placeholder=\"密码\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"checkbox\">\r\n                    <label>\r\n                        <input type=\"checkbox\"> Remember me\r\n                    </label>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-default\">Sign in</button>\r\n            </form>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n            \r\n            <h3>水平排列的表单</h3>\r\n            \r\n            <form class=\"form-horizontal\" role=\"form\">\r\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                    <label for=\"inputEmail3\" class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">电子邮箱</label>\r\n                    <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\r\n                        <input type=\"email\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"inputEmail3\" placeholder=\"电子邮箱\">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                    <label for=\"inputPassword3\" class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">密码</label>\r\n                    <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\r\n                        <input type=\"password\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"inputPassword3\" placeholder=\"密码\">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                    <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\r\n                        <div class=\"checkbox\">\r\n                            <label>\r\n                                <input type=\"checkbox\"> Remember me\r\n                            </label>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                    <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\r\n                        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-default\">Sign in</button>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </form>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>','.row{\r\n    margin: 15px 0;\r\n}\r\n.row > div{\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n    border: 1px solid #DDD;\r\n    border-radius: 10px;\r\n    \r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n    \r\n    background-color: #efefef;\r\n}','','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css,../script/lib/bootstrap/bootstrap-3.0.2/js/bootstrap.min.js','Bootstrap 框架实践-5 表单',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',NULL,NULL,'2014-01-03 11:28:55',NULL,NULL,'4,98,137','UI,Bootstrap,编程实践');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (154,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>D3 数据可视化-10</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"testTarget\" id=\"testTarget\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    var dataset = [5, 10, 20, 45, 6, 25],\r\n        \r\n        height = 300,\r\n        width = 300,\r\n        \r\n        innerRadius = 0,    // 若 内弧度不为 0，则图形为变成环形\r\n        outerRadius = width /2,\r\n        \r\n        color = d3.scale.category10(),\r\n        \r\n        arc = d3.svg.arc().innerRadius( innerRadius ).outerRadius( outerRadius ),\r\n        \r\n        // d3.layout.pie() d3 布局方法 饼状图\r\n        pie = d3.layout.pie(),\r\n            \r\n        svg = d3.select(\'#testTarget\').append(\'svg\').attr({\r\n            width: width,\r\n            height: height\r\n        }),\r\n            \r\n        // 准备分组\r\n        arcs = svg.selectAll(\'g.arc\').data( pie( dataset ) ).enter().append(\'g\').attr({\r\n            \'class\': \'arc\',\r\n            transform: \'translate(\'+ outerRadius +\',\'+ outerRadius +\')\'\r\n        });\r\n    \r\n    // 绘制弧形路径\r\n    arcs.append(\'path\').attr({\r\n        fill: function(d, i){\r\n            return color(i);\r\n        },\r\n        d: arc\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    arcs.append(\'text\').attr({\r\n        transform: function(d){\r\n            return \'translate(\'+ arc.centroid(d) +\')\';\r\n            // arc.centroid(d) 计算并返回任何弧形的中心点\r\n        },\r\n        \'text-anchor\': \'middle\'\r\n    }).text(function(d){\r\n        return d.value;\r\n    });\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/d3/d3.v3.min.js','D3 数据可视化-10',NULL,'../image/preview/d3-10.jpg',NULL,NULL,'2014-01-03 14:44:39',NULL,NULL,'55,97,104','数据可视化,D3.js,SVG');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (155,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>D3 数据可视化-11</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"testTarget\" id=\"testTarget\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.case h3{\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n    \r\n    /*\r\n    var dataset = [\r\n        {apples: 5,    oranges: 10,    grapes: 22},\r\n        {apples: 4,    oranges: 12,    grapes: 28},\r\n        {apples: 2,    oranges: 19,    grapes: 32},\r\n        {apples: 7,    oranges: 23,    grapes: 35},\r\n        {apples: 23,   oranges: 17,    grapes: 43}\r\n    ];\r\n     */\r\n    var dataset = [\r\n        [\r\n            {x: 0, y: 5}, {x: 1, y: 4}, {x: 2, y: 2}, {x: 3, y: 7}, {x: 4, y: 23}\r\n        ], [\r\n            {x: 0, y: 10}, {x: 1, y: 12}, {x: 2, y: 19}, {x: 3, y: 23}, {x: 4, y: 17}\r\n        ], [\r\n            {x: 0, y: 22}, {x: 1, y: 28}, {x: 2, y: 32}, {x: 3, y: 35}, {x: 4, y: 43}\r\n        ]\r\n    ];\r\n    \r\n    var height = 300,\r\n        width = 500,\r\n        \r\n        color = d3.scale.category10(),\r\n        \r\n        // d3.layout.stack() d3 布局方法 堆叠布局\r\n        stack = d3.layout.stack(),\r\n    \r\n        svg = d3.select(\'#testTarget\').append(\'svg\').attr({\r\n            width: width,\r\n            height: height\r\n        });\r\n        \r\n    stack( dataset );\r\n        \r\n    var xScale = d3.scale.ordinal().domain(d3.range(dataset[0].length)).rangeRoundBands([0, width], 0.05),\r\n        yScale = d3.scale.linear().domain([0, d3.max(dataset, function(d){\r\n            return d3.max(d, function(d){\r\n                return d.y0 + d.y;\r\n            });\r\n        })]).range([0, height]),\r\n        \r\n        groups = svg.selectAll(\'g\').data( dataset ).enter().append(\'g\').style(\'fill\', function(d, i){\r\n            return color(i);\r\n        });\r\n    \r\n    groups.selectAll(\'rect\').data(function(d){\r\n        return d;\r\n    }).enter().append(\'rect\').attr({\r\n        x: function(d, i){\r\n            return xScale(i);\r\n        },\r\n        y: function(d, i){\r\n            return yScale(d.y0);\r\n        },\r\n        height: function(d){\r\n            return yScale(d.y);\r\n        },\r\n        width: xScale.rangeBand()\r\n    });\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/lib/d3/d3.v3.min.js','D3 数据可视化-11',NULL,'../image/preview/d3-11.jpg',NULL,NULL,'2014-01-03 15:47:25',NULL,NULL,'55,104,97','数据可视化,SVG,D3.js');
INSERT INTO `editor` VALUES (156,'<div class=\"case\">\r\n    <h3>JS 插件-RSS 订阅[第三方]</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <p>插件中使用了 Google Feeds API，若其 Down 掉或无法连接，后果很糟糕。。。\r\n       \r\n        <br />\r\n        <br />更多参考\r\n        <a href=\"http://www.jquery-plugins.net/FeedEK/FeedEk.html\">\r\n            http://www.jquery-plugins.net/FeedEK/FeedEk.html\r\n        </a>\r\n    </p>\r\n    \r\n    <div id=\"rssTest1\" class=\"rssTest\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"rssTest2\" class=\"rssTest\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"rssTest3\" class=\"rssTest\"></div>\r\n</div>','.case{\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n    border: 5px solid #c0c0c0;\r\n    margin: 10px;\r\n    padding: 10px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.rssTest{\r\n    float: left;\r\n    margin-right: 10px;\r\n}','$(function(){\r\n\r\n    $(\'#rssTest1\').FeedEk({\r\n        FeedUrl: \'http://www.36kr.com/feed/\',\r\n        MaxCount: 20,\r\n        DescCharacterLimit: 100\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#rssTest2\').FeedEk({\r\n        FeedUrl: \'http://www.huxiu.com/rss/0.xml\',\r\n        MaxCount: 5,\r\n        ShowDesc: true,\r\n        ShowPubDate: false,\r\n        DescCharacterLimit: 100\r\n    });\r\n    \r\n    $(\'#rssTest3\').FeedEk({\r\n        FeedUrl: \'http://feeds.geekpark.net/\',\r\n        MaxCount: 5,\r\n        ShowDesc: false\r\n    });\r\n});','../script/lib/jQuery/jquery-1.10.2.min.js,../script/plugin/FeedEk/FeedEk.css,../script/plugin/FeedEk/FeedEk.js','JS 插件-RSS 订阅[第三方]',NULL,'../image/default/no-pic.png',NULL,NULL,'2014-01-04 10:54:39',NULL,NULL,'122','jQuery 插件');
